    2001: "Gold",
    2002: "A pair of Revolvers favored by members of the mafia for their classic profile. It's very quick to draw and fire, which is important when one shot may be all you need.",
    2003: "Dark Divination Two-Handed Sword",
    2004: "Check",
    2005: "Homestead Fairy Flower Patch (Partial)",
    2006: "Gold",
    2007: "A wig that resembles the beautiful hair of the Iceborn Noble who exists deep within the snowy mountains. It's imbued with magic and displays a special effect.",
    2008: "Homestead Fairy Flower Garden",
    2009: "요리사 아일린 말풍선 스티커(30일)",
    2010: "연회장 직원 아일린 말풍선 스티커(30일)",
    2011: "말풍선을 꾸밀 수 있는 기사 아일린 스티커. 마우스 오른쪽 버튼 클릭 후 '사용하기' 를 선택해서 사용하면 말풍선에 붙일 수 있다. 스티커는 30일간 유지된다.",
    2012: "말풍선을 꾸밀 수 있는 요리사 아일린 스티커. 마우스 오른쪽 버튼 클릭 후 '사용하기' 를 선택해서 사용하면 말풍선에 붙일 수 있다. 스티커는 30일간 유지된다.",
    2013: "말풍선을 꾸밀 수 있는 연회장 직원 아일린 스티커. 마우스 오른쪽 버튼 클릭 후 '사용하기' 를 선택해서 사용하면 말풍선에 붙일 수 있다. 스티커는 30일간 유지된다.",
    2014: "아이템 가방(200)",
    2015: "핀 싱크 수련 포션",
    2016: "Fir Bolg Gloves",
    2017: "The outfit of a keen witness who observes the world. Made for travel, it's perfect for one who seeks new experiences in the world around them. Sometimes, the best guide is one who's simply read all the signposts.",
    2018: "The outfit of a wanderer who seeks the truth of the world. Made for travel, it's perfect for one who doesn't know where they'll end up next. Perhaps a guide could be just around the corner.",
    2019: "A pair of boots for a keen witness who observes the world. Supportive soles are perfect for one set on their path.",
    2020: "Broad-brimmed Belted Hat",
    2021: "Slouchy Belted Beret",
    2022: "A broad-brimmed hat decorated with a feather and a belt. It's perfect to keep the sun off your face on the open road.",
    2023: "A beret decorated with a buckle and a belt. It's perfect to keep your head warm when the wind gets cold.",
    2024: "Balloon Lance Appearance Scroll",
    2025: "A pair of stylish gloves designed by Ailionoa. Their understated design is accented with small, metal ornaments.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    2026: "A pair of stylish gloves designed by Ailionoa. They're decorated with a lacy floral pattern.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    2027: "Registered Bond",
    2028: "Part of the Hebona set, said to enhance the fundamental Bolt Magic spells. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater magical power.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
