    8501: "Place this Übel figure in your Homestead for a little boost to your stats.\n[*Protection: +1]\n(Effects cannot be stacked. Stat increase will disappear if taken down.)",
    8502: "몽상의 쉼터",
    8503: "몽상 속에 있는 것 같은 아름다운 초승달 형태의 의자. 밤의 주인이 휴식을 취할 때 온다고 한다. 사용 시 느긋하게 앉아 휴식을 취할 수 있다.",
    8504: "Do the colors available to you fall short of meeting your exacting expectations? Take matters into your own hands! Use this mold to create your own Stardust Dye Ampoule with colors mixed just the way you like them. It disappears after a single use.",
    8505: "Do the colors available to you fall short of meeting your exacting expectations? Take matters into your own hands! Use this mold to create your own Pet Dye Ampoule with colors mixed just the way you like them. It disappears after a single use.",
    8506: "DIY Flashy Dye Mold (Not tradable)",
    8507: "DIY Flashy Dye Ampoule",
    8508: "Do the colors available to you fall short of meeting your exacting expectations? Take matters into your own hands! Use this mold to create your own Flashy Dye Ampoule with colors mixed just the way you like them. It disappears after a single use.",
    8509: "You can use this ampoule to paint a single part of an item with a specified color. Unlike regular dye ampoules, it will apply the exact color listed. It disappears after a single use. (Not tradable)",
    8510: "Damage Skin - Witch's Brew",
