    12058: "Baltane Seal Ring",
    12100: "A badge to salute your achievement on the advancement test. When you have a skill at Dan 3 or higher, you can collect badges and take them to the Advancement Guide to use the [Custom Combo Card] function.",
    12101: "A scented candle that features a fresh lemongrass aroma. Mainly sold at Healer's Houses, its citrus scent will produce a special effect when you burn it in a campfire and rest nearby.\n\n* Fishing success rate and Fish Size Adjustment +2",
    12102: "A scented candle that features a fresh lemongrass aroma. More wax has been added, making it larger than a mini candle. Its citrus scent will produce a special effect when you burn it in a campfire and rest nearby.\n\n* Fishing success rate and Fish Size Adjustment +5",
    12103: "A scented candle that features a fresh lemongrass aroma. A catalyst has been added to the fine candle to create a truly scent-sual experience. Its citrus scent will produce a special effect when you burn it in a campfire and rest nearby.\n\n* Fishing Success Rate and Fish Size Adjustment +10",
    12104: "A chair you can use while fishing. It is sturdy enough that you'll stay in place no matter how hard a fish pulls.",
