    12107: "Erg EXP Fragment (15000)",
    12108: "Erg EXP Fragment (40000)",
    12109: "A gem created when large amounts of Hope Essence have been materialized. A strong impulse of desire seems to throb from somewhere within the translucent jewel.\nAllows you to perform a guaranteed upgrade to Rank 2 on a Rank 3 item that can be reforged.",
    12110: "A fragment of a crystal that hums with energy. When placed in an Additional Material slot during Erg Infusion, it will yield 3,000 EXP.",
