    13000: "The beautiful horn of a unicorn. Colors seem to dance across its surface, and one can even see a glow emanating from it at night.",
    13001: "Dreamseer's Unicorn Crossbow",
    13002: "Dreamseer's Unicorn Lance",
    13003: "A crossbow created from the powerful horn of a unicorn. It shines with steadfast purity, ornamented with roses.",
    13004: "A lance created from the powerful horn of a unicorn. It shines with steadfast purity, ornamented with roses.",
    13005: "Destroyer's Blade",
    13006: "Cethlenn's Staff",
    13007: "Destroyer's Blade",
    13008: "Cethlenn's Staff",
    13009: "Graffiti Cylinder",
    13010: "Graffiti Spray Paint",
    13011: "An alchemical cylinder tagged with colorful graffiti. It can be used to fire alchemy crystals. Given how prevalent the graffiti is, you won't notice if it gets a scratch or two in battle.",
    13012: "A surprisingly heavy can of spray paint for the aspiring graffiti artist. Use Smash to spray it if you need to use a stronger attack.",
    13013: "Troubadour's Bowharp",
    13014: "Troubadour's Chalumeau Cylinder",
    13015: "Troubadour's Violin Guard Cylinder",
    13016: "A bow specially crafted for bards who sometimes stride onto the field of battle. It's strung with harp strings along the inner curve so that musicians can strum the notes of their potent songs in between well-aimed shots.",
    13017: "A cylinder specially crafted for bards who also seek to plumb the mysteries of alchemy. Designed to resemble a chalumeau, it can be used to fire alchemy crystals, though it seems like it could be blown to play a beautiful tune at any moment.",
    13018: "A defensive Cylinder specially crafted for bards who also seek to plumb the mysteries of alchemy. Designed to resemble a violin, it appears as though one could take a bow to its strings to play a beautiful tune. A beautiful shield is attached to the cylinder, allowing you to use powerful Alchemy skills while protecting yourself, especially from magical attacks. Without a cylinder, some of your Alchemy skills will be limited.",
    13019: "Swansong Wand",
    13020: "A lithe, agile wand topped with an alabaster carving of a graceful swan. It lends the bird's regal grace to the time-honored art of magic.",
    13021: "Royal Guardian Hammer",
    13022: "An ornate hammer used ceremonially by royal knights. Even under the veil of night, its glowing gems illuminate the darkness.",
    13023: "Elegant earrings inspired by black roses. You can equip them along with some hat items.",
    13024: "An elegant left earring and monocle inspired by black roses. You can equip them along with some hat items.",
    13025: "Elegant wings inspired by black roses. You can see the beauty of snow crystals within them. Can be dyed. (Can be enchanted)",
    13026: "Elegant wings inspired by black roses. You can see the beauty of snow crystals within them. (Can be enchanted)",
    13027: "Enchanting Peacock Wine Glass",
    13028: "Peacock's Visage Handled Masque",
    13029: "Enchanting Peacock Parasol",
    13030: "Enchanting Peacock Grimoire",
    13031: "순수한 로열 프리모 헤일로",
    13032: "영롱한 로열 프리모 헤일로",
    13033: "고요한 로열 프리모 헤일로",
    13034: "심오한 마법의 섭리를 깨닫고 배열한 마법진 헤일로. 정교하게 짜인 빛의 문양이 경이로운 분위기를 연출한다.",
    13035: "Special Aura's Outfit (F)",
    13036: "Special Linie's Outfit (F)",
    13037: "Special Lugner's Outfit (M)",
