    14000: "A fluted wine glass styled in a peacock motif. The metal pattern around the rim and the turquoise gemstones set in it make every sip feel all the richer.",
    14001: "An ornate masque decorated with feathers, designed to conceal one's identity at masquerade balls and costume parties. You may hide your face, but can you truly avoid drawing attention with so fine an accessory?",
    14002: "An elegant all-weather umbrella styled in a peacock motif. It's ready to shield you from scorching sun and pouring rain, and even looks fabulous folded up.",
    14003: "A mystic spell book from a distant land, styled in a peacock motif. The turquoise gem on its spine acts as a conduit for the flow of magical energies.",
    14004: "Destroyer's Blade",
    14005: "Destroyer's Blade",
    14006: "Lightning Sword",
    14007: "A one-handed sword infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning.",
    14008: "Runic Cheek Decoration (Facewear)",
    14009: "Runic Forehead Decoration (Facewear)",
    14010: "Merchants' Guild Abacus",
    14011: "An abacus large enough to serve as a proper bludgeon, which also has the beneficial side effect of discouraging shoplifters. Hits with all the force of local taxes!",
    14012: "로즈 템테이션 부케",
    14013: "로즈 템테이션 클러치 백",
    14014: "우아한 검은 장미를 중심으로 엮은 꽃다발. 들고 다니면 우아한 아름다움을 느낄 수 있다.",
    14015: "Virtuous Wonderland Alice Pocket Watch Frame",
    14016: "로즈 템테이션 보우",
    14017: "로즈 템테이션 스태프",
    14018: "The shoes of a resistance fighter who never gives in to tyranny. They're designed to give you an extra edge, necessary for those who plan to keep fighting until the bitter end.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    14019: "Falcon of Sunrise Gloves (F) (Rental)",
    14020: "Magnolia Classic Braided Hair Beauty Coupon (M)",
    14021: "Bleiddian Hair Beauty Coupon (M)",
    14022: "Savvy Socialite Hair Beauty Coupon (M)",
    14023: "스트라이프 패턴의 베이직한 남성 수영복",
    14024: "깜찍한 레이스가 찰랑거리는 귀여운 여성 수영복",
    14025: "A scroll that changes a weapon's appearance to that of a Shadow Reaper Shuriken. You can only use it on a shuriken. (Cannot be used on Classic Spirit Weapons or other select weapons.) The scroll will disappear once the effect has been applied.",
    14026: "Cowenna Figure",
    14027: "Fine Constellation Bait",
    14028: "A book containing all the fundamental things an adventurer in Erinn ought to know about handling the rigors of combat. Right-click to read it.",
    14029: "A book containing all the fundamental things an adventurer in Erinn ought to know about crafting, gathering, and other tasks that make up daily living. Right-click to read it.",
    14030: "@Giant Shoulder Armor",
    14031: "@Odelia Pin Armor",
    14032: "@Stitched Long Robe Armor",
    14033: "@Terra V-line Four-point Armor",
    14034: "@Spark Leather Armor",
    14035: "Visit Eavan at Dunbarton's Town Office to purchase a Ciar Advanced Hard Mode Dungeon Reward Box from the Dungeon Reward Shop.",
    14036: "Winter Wolf Box",
    14037: "A box containing clothing and gear worn by the Winter Wolves, a famous band of warriors hailing from the snowbound northern reaches of the world. Use it to obtain one of a variety of items (probability varies by item), including a Special Winter Wolf Outfit (M), Special Winter Wolf Outfit (F), Regal Wolf Greatsword Appearance Scroll, Regal Wolf Lance Appearance Scroll, and Regal Wolf Shield Appearance Scroll.",
    14038: "A special blend of warm, flavorful spices perfectly suited to many baking recipes, requested by Ancon to \"buff the power\" of their cookie recipe. Glenis assures you that adding a pinch or two as you're folding the dough will make your batch of cookies turn out especially delicious.\n\n* This item will be removed at 7:00 AM (Server Time) every day.",
    14039: "Doki Doki Flower Doll (Critical Totem)",
    14040: "Doki Doki Grandpa Doll (Max HP Totem)",
    14041: "Doki Doki Grandma Doll (Max MP Totem)",
    14042: "A card that changes the visual effect of the Death Mark skill. Right-click and select 'Activate' to turn on the Angry Bear effect. Each character can only possess one such effect-altering card.",
    14043: "Wild Eclipse Long Hair Beauty Coupon (M)",
    14044: "썬더 스킬을 사용했을 때 이펙트가 달라지는 카드. 마우스 오른쪽 버튼 클릭 후 '활성화'를 선택하면 블러디 일렉트릭 테크 외형의 이펙트를 확인할 수 있다. 이펙트 변경 카드는 캐릭터 당 1개만 가질 수 있다.",
    14045: "Turban Shell Armor (F)",
    14046: "Turban Shell Armor (M)",
    14047: "Flame Patterned Leather Armor (M)",
    14048: "Flame Patterned Leather Armor (F)",
