    15188: "@Odelia Unbalanced Armor",
    15189: "Delaney's Fluffy Friend",
    15190: "A creamy, slightly sweet soup filled with plenty of corn. Delaney asked Neal to make it, hoping that its power to bring to mind happy memories for her might work its magic on someone else.",
    15191: "@Kira Floral-Patterned Robe",
