    15201: "Erinn Explorer's Map",
    15202: "A covered wagon that recalls tales of pioneers crossing open plains. Place it on your Homestead to be protected from the elements--just watch out for dysentery.",
    15203: "A welcoming facade for a wild west saloon. Place it on your homestead to declare to visitors that this town IS big enough for the both of you.",
    15204: "A model airship so realistic that Lorna and Pan showed up to take a ride. Place it on your Homestead to sail the skies of Erinn from the comfort of your own home.",
    15205: "DIY Dye Mold (Not tradable)",
    15206: "DIY Metal Dye Mold (Not tradable)",
    15207: "Place this Serie figure in your Homestead for a little boost to your stats.\n[*Magic Protection: +1]\n(Effects cannot be stacked. Stat increase will disappear if taken down.)",
