    15212: "2024 Black Combo Card Returns Gold Reset Count Hidden Item",
    15213: "A material Tito gave you. Use your Handicraft skill to make a Tree Decoration out of it.\n\n* This item will be deleted when the events ends.",
    15214: "A decoration you can use to adorn a tree.\n\n* This item will be deleted when the events ends.",
    15215: "Enchanted Metal",
    15216: "Enchanted Ore Fragment",
    15217: "A string possessing incredibly high tensile strength that also allows for delicate control of a variety of energies.\n\nProduced through Handicraft, and can be used as a crafting material.",
    15218: "Dull Blade Fragment",
    15219: "A card that changes the visual effect of the Spellwalk skill. Right-click and select 'Activate' to turn on the Pink Rose effect. Each character can only possess one such effect-altering card.",
    15220: "Homestead Rowan Portrait Easel",
    15221: "An easel that can be placed on your Homestead. This easel displays a portrait of Rowan of the Arcana Association.",
    15222: "Dull Blade Fragment (Not tradable)",
    15223: "Verdant Mage's Gem (Not tradable)",
    15224: "Hard Wolf Tooth (Not tradable)",
    15225: "Mana Stone (Not tradable)",
    15226: "Shard of Solace Stardust",
    15227: "A bottle containing the strange power of Shard of Solace Stardust, which becomes available when you use this item. When the Shard of Solace Stardust becomes available, Stardust Support Effect Damage is increased by 10%.\n\n(If you have multiple Stardust Support Effect Damage Increase bonuses, only the highest value will be applied.)",
    15228: "@Giant Newbie Wear (F)",
    15229: "@Premium Newbie Wear (F)",
    15230: "@Garten Glen Checkered Skirt",
    15231: "Adamantine Coin",
    15232: "A colorful token earned by clearing dungeons and other challenges listed in the Dungeon Guide. Eavan at Dunbarton's Town Office will accept these coins in trade for items in her Fourth Shop.",
    15233: "Elegant Gothic Dress Long Type",
    15234: "A pass that, when used, reduces the tally for the number of times you have received weekly rewards from Glenn Bearna by 1, allowing you to obtain rewards an additional time. Cannot be used until you have received Glenn Bearna rewards at least once this week.",
    15235: "Elegant Gothic Dress Short Type",
    15236: "[Magic Attack Totem]\nA totem that twinkles with the hopeful light of a small star just before sunrise. When placed in your inventory, it will boost your Magic Attack. Right-click and select \"Activate\" to turn the effect on. (Totems of the same type cannot be activated together)",
    15237: "[Critical Totem]\nA totem that twinkles with the hopeful light of a small star just before sunrise. When placed in your inventory, it will boost your Critical Hit Rate. Right-click and select \"Activate\" to turn the effect on. (Totems of the same type cannot be activated together)",
    15238: "[Movement Speed Totem]\nA totem that twinkles with the hopeful light of a small star just before sunrise. When placed in your inventory, it will boost your Movement Speed. Right-click and select \"Activate\" to turn the effect on. (Totems of the same type cannot be activated together)",
    15239: "[Max HP Totem]\nA totem that twinkles with the hopeful light of a small star just before sunrise. When placed in your inventory, it will boost your Max HP. Right-click and select \"Activate\" to turn the effect on. (Totems of the same type cannot be activated together)",
    15240: "Warrior Corgi Whistle (Medal Storage Unavailable)",
    15241: "A whistle that calls forth a Warrior Corgi!\n\nThis pet cannot be stored in a Pet Adoption Medal.",
    15242: "Exclusive Voight Outfit",
    15243: "우리들의 친구인 동물을 만날 수 있는 기회. 사랑스런 무등고래를 만나보세요.\n획득한 펫은 동물 캐릭터 분양 메달에 담을 수 없습니다.",
