    15267: "Remy's Alby Dungeon Pass",
    15268: "An Alby Dungeon Pass received from Remy. Offer it on the altar in front of the Goddess Statue in the lobby of the Alby Dungeon to enter. If you lose it, you can receive another from Remy.",
    15269: "A colored stone used to perform special upgrades on equipment that has already received a Gem Upgrade, and which is currently below Level 5. Red Upgrade Stones increase the damage dealt by Critical Hits. This Upgrade Stone guarantees a successful upgrade.\n\n<color=1>* It can only be used on Fergseus weapons from the event.</color>",
    15270: "Antidote Potion for Teenagers",
    15271: "A page of notes written by Laoire, giving further details pertaining to a routine patrol request. Its folds are sharp and crisp, indicative of an individual with a true gift for paperwork.",
    15272: "A detailed blueprint depicting the ultimate firearm conceived by Micheil. Its complexities far exceed a normal person's ability to comprehend.",
    15273: "A book obtained from the Scary Library with Taise.\n......",
