    15275: "Cat Suit",
    15276: "특별한 손수건을 사용하여 특별한 코인을 획득했다. 모아둔 코인으로 여러가지 아이템을 교환할 수 있다.",
    15277: "Starline Asterism Scythe Appearance Scroll",
    15278: "A scroll that changes a weapon's appearance to that of a Starline Asterism Scythe. You can only use it on a scythe. (Cannot be used on Classic Spirit Weapons or other select weapons.) The scroll will disappear once the effect has been applied.",
    15279: "Spirit Transformation Liqueur (Sacred Guardian)",
    15280: "Homestead Special Masterpiece Scene Vol. 4",
    15281: "Place this Masterpiece Scene Vol. 3 on your Homestead to relive the three lost warriors' legendary fight. This limited edition print also gives a small increase to your stats.\n[*Defense: +3, Protection +3, Critical Damage: +9%]\n(Effects cannot be stacked. The stat increase will disappear if this item is removed from the Homestead.)",
    15282: "Magical Baaaaa Compact",
    15283: "Magical Raccooo Compact",
