    15285: "A Beauty Coupon that allows you to change your hair for free in the Dressing Room under Appearance Change. (Not tradable)",
    15286: "@Premium Giant Winter Newbie Wear (M)",
    15287: "Rebirth Potion Trophy",
    15288: "A trophy that commemorates the accomplishment of Milletians who have reached 1 million cumulative levels. Its pulsing colors honor the Milletian Pluse00, the first in the North American region to reach this milestone. A small note is attached, expressing the admiration of the development team.\n\n<color=1>In appreciation for your dedication and passion in reaching 1 million levels, we gratefully bestow upon you this trophy in honor of the Rebirth Potions that have fueled your long journey.\n- The Mabinogi Team</color>",
    15289: "Festive Eastern Box",
    15290: "A box that contains clothing and items that call to mind the happiest and most beautiful memories of a spring festival. Use it to obtain one of a variety of items (probability varies by item), including Special Festive Eastern Wear (M), Special Festive Eastern Dress (F), Festive Eastern Umbrella Halo, Festive Eastern Lantern Staff Appearance Scroll, and Festive Eastern Fireworks Lance Appearance Scroll.",
    15291: "Primitive Stone Axe (Hammer) Appearance Scroll",
    15292: "크림슨 녹턴 코인",
    15293: "특별한 상자를 개봉하여 특별한 코인을 획득했다. 모아둔 코인으로 여러가지 아이템을 교환할 수 있다.",
    15294: "Tech Duinn Mission Additional Entry Pass",
    15295: "Tech Duinn Mission Additional Entry Pass",
