    16564: "A ring made with an extremely rare heart gem. While it may be great for those who've made a lifelong promise of love, it may not be so great for singles. It doesn't look very great with clothes that cover your wrists.\n\n(Cannot be repaired or enchanted)",
    16565: "A watch and strap of the sort popularly worn when one is going out for the day. With a relaxed yet tidy appearance, they complement a variety of casual looks without drawing too much attention.",
    16566: "A watch of the sort popularly worn when one is going out for the day. With a relaxed yet tidy appearance, it complements a variety of casual looks without drawing too much attention.",
    16567: "A pair of sturdy boots perfect for walking wherever your day's adventures take you. They're comfy enough to wear every day and durable enough to hold up mile after mile.",
