    16606: "A magical bag that can summon a special Rainy Day Duckling Doll. You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when summoned with a Rainy Day Gosling Doll. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 10x9\nDoll Summon Time: 120 min.\nDoll Weight: 0.3 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +8, Max Damage +8, Strength +10, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +5\nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Enchant Scrolls, Fynni Gems",
