    16617: "This magical bag can summon the Dorren and Eabha dolls together! You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when the dolls are summoned. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 11x11\nDoll Summon Time: 140 min.\nDoll Weight: 0.7 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +10, Max Damage +10, Magic Attack +4, Strength/Dexterity +20, Intelligence/Will/Luck +10, Critical +4, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +5, Attack Speed +1%, Movement Speed +1%, Critical Damage +2%\nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Alchemy Crystals/Cuilin Stones, Rare Mineralogy, Shyllien Ecology",
    16618: "This magical bag can summon the Brenda and Pierrick dolls together! You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when the dolls are summoned. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 11x11\nDoll Summon Time: 140 min.\nDoll Weight: 0.7 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +12, Max Damage +19, Magic Attack +5, Strength/Dexterity +15, Intelligence +8, Will/Luck +10, Critical +3, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +5, Combat EXP +15%, Gathering Speed +3%, Critical Damage +1% \nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Weaving/Sheep Shearing, Tailoring Materials, Dye Ampoules, Hoeing, Firewood, Gems, Small Colored Gems",
    16619: "This magical bag can summon the Rainy Day Duckling and Gosling dolls together! You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when the dolls are summoned. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 12x11\nDoll Summon Time: 180 min.\nDoll Weight: 0.7 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +12, Max Damage +20, Magic Attack +5, Strength/Dexterity +10, Intelligence +12, Will/Luck +5, Critical +2, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +6, Attack Speed +3%, Movement Speed +2%\nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Enchant Scrolls, Fynni Gems, Passes, Fomor Scrolls",
    16620: "This magical bag can summon the Dorren, Eabha, Brenda, and Pierrick dolls together! You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when the dolls are summoned. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 13x13\nDoll Summon Time: 150 min.\nDoll Weight: 1 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +15, Max Damage +22, Magic Attack +9, Strength/Intelligence +17, Dexterity +20, Will/Luck +15, Critical +5, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +7, Critical Damage +3%, Attack Speed +3%, Movement Speed +2%, Gathering Speed +3%\nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Alchemy Crystals/Cuilin Stones, Rare Mineralogy, Shyllien Ecology, Weaving/Sheep Shearing, Tailoring Materials, Dye Ampoules, Hoeing, Firewood, Gems, Small Colored Gems",
    16621: "This magical bag can summon the Dorren, Eabha, Brenda, and Pierrick dolls together! You can summon a doll separately from a pet. A set effect activates when the dolls are summoned. To use ventriloquy on the doll, use the command \"/Doll[order number] [line]\" in the chat window. (Example: /Doll1 Hello!)\n\n<color=3>[Doll Bag Info]</color>\nBag Size: 13x13\nDoll Summon Time: 150 min.\nDoll Weight: 1 (Dolls can be summoned up to a total weight of 1)\nSummon Effect: Min Damage +15, Max Damage +22, Magic Attack +9, Strength/Intelligence +17, Dexterity +20, Will/Luck +15, Critical +5, Protection/Defense/Magic Protection/Magic Defense +7, Critical Damage +3%, Attack Speed +3%, Movement Speed +2%, Gathering Speed +3%\nDoll Collection Categories: Gold, Alchemy Crystals/Cuilin Stones, Rare Mineralogy, Shyllien Ecology, Weaving/Sheep Shearing, Tailoring Materials, Dye Ampoules, Hoeing, Firewood, Gems, Small Colored Gems",
    16622: "Taillteann Townspeople Doll Bag Box",
    16623: "Taillteann Townspeople Doll Bag Box",
    16624: "A special box containing a variety of cute and handy doll bags. You might find familiar faces from around Taillteann. Use it to obtain one of a variety of items (probability varies by item), including Taillteann Townspeople Compact Doll Bag Box, Rainy Day Duckling Premium Doll Bag Box, Rainy Day Gosling Premium Doll Bag Box, Dorren Doll Bag Box, Eabha Doll Bag Box, Brenda Doll Bag Box, and Pierrick Doll Bag Box.",
    16625: "A special box containing a variety of cute and handy doll bags. You might find familiar faces from around Taillteann. Use it to obtain one of a variety of items (probability varies by item), including Taillteann Townspeople Compact Doll Bag Box, Rainy Day Duckling Premium Doll Bag Box, Rainy Day Gosling Premium Doll Bag Box, Dorren Doll Bag Box, Eabha Doll Bag Box, Brenda Doll Bag Box, and Pierrick Doll Bag Box.",
