    17500: "Sacred Glow Holy Water",
    17501: "A scroll that contains orders and decrees written by high-ranking inquisitors. It's said that if it is read by an enemy, the text will burn off.",
    17502: "A censer that gives off a sacred glow. The scent is divine.",
    17503: "Holy water that gives off a sacred glow. It's as pure as the finest crystal.",
    17504: "Glittering Fairy Wing Fan",
    17505: "Fairy Bubble Blower",
    17506: "A big fan designed to resemble a fairy's wings. The glimmering sparkles capture the attention of fae and humans alike.",
    17507: "A wand for blowing bubbles that has been enchanted to scatter fairy dust instead. You'll find the sparkles everywhere on your clothes and in your hair--likely just as the fairies intended.",
    17508: "Casual Tech Chic Dual Guns",
    17509: "Casual Tech Chic Messenger Bag",
    17510: "A glowing circle that captures the ebb and flow of light. Soothing and entrancing to watch, they are found in a variety of colors, each said to hold its own meaning.",
    17511: "This Messenger Bag is made out of steel-infused fibers, making it resistant to all kinds of dangers. It will keep your most important equipment safe on a top-secret mission.",
    17512: "스페셜 코트 스타일링 수트(남성용)",
    17513: "Special Sunbather's Bliss Wear (M)",
    17514: "Special Sunbather's Bliss Wear (F)",
    17515: "A pair of boots worn by the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next. They impart a certain quiet gravity to the wearer's footfalls.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    17516: "Sunbather's Paradise Wear (M)",
    17517: "Etching this signet onto your Celtic Royal Warrior Axe will amplify its power. It can be used on a Celtic Royal Warrior Axe with level 5 or higher Signet Effect to level up its Signet Effect by 1.",
    17518: "칠흑 같은 어둠과 닮은 듯한 차분한 가발. 입을 가려주는 마스크가 한층 더 정체를 알 수 없게 만들어 준다.",
    17519: "Ricotta cheese salad, one of Doki Doki Island's signature dishes. The combination of savory ricotta cheese and fresh vegetables makes for a hearty and healthy meal.\nYou could just eat it, of course, but you can also use it as a Catering ingredient.",
    17520: "Clothing perfect for avid readers ready to lose hours in the pages of a new book. Its fashionable look will serve you well from the quiet tables in the library to the lively tables of the nearby cafe.",
    17521: "스트라이프를 메인 테마로 한 과감한 여성 수영복",
    17522: "봉인된 지배자의 낫 외형 주문서",
    17523: "A scroll that changes a weapon's appearance to that of a Noble Golf Club. You can only use it on a staff. (Cannot be used on Classic Spirit Weapons or other select weapons.) The scroll will disappear once the effect has been applied.",
    17524: "Divine Link Effect Change Card (Lovely Butterflies)",
    17525: "Digital Destiny Hair Beauty Coupon (M)",
    17526: "배쉬 스킬을 사용했을 때 이펙트가 달라지는 카드. 마우스 오른쪽 버튼 클릭 후 '활성화'를 선택하면 루미나 퓨어 스페이스 외형의 이펙트를 확인할 수 있다. 이펙트 변경 카드는 캐릭터 당 1개만 가질 수 있다.",
    17527: "@Basil Gimlet Greaves",
    17528: "@Colin Plate Boots",
    17529: "@Fluted Plate Greaves",
    17530: "Dragon Scale Greaves",
    17531: "Exquisite Arashi Greaves (M)",
    17532: "Exquisite Arashi Greaves (F)",
