    18500: "NPC Eochaid's Staff",
    18501: "The staff that Eochaid usually carries with him, capable of casting all three types of elemental magic. It greatly amplifies the wielder's magical power by accumulating the residual mana left from all the spells cast by its bearer.",
    18502: "NPC Cowenna's Sword",
    18503: "Cowenna's personal blade. Stalwartly unbroken, but not for lack of force.",
    18504: "Marvelous Merch Cart",
    18505: "Lemonade Cart",
    18506: "Shorebreak Surfboard",
    18507: "A cart full of whimsical merchandise to peddle as you move from place to place. There's sure to be something that'll catch your eye!",
    18508: "A cart designed to provide the entire lemonade experience, from fresh-picked lemons to ice-cold glasses. Deliver refined refreshment, every time.",
    18509: "A surfboard that bears the image of waves washing over a sandy beach. It has been enchanted with magic that allows it to be used even on land.",
    18510: "Dark Nightstorm Devil Wings",
    18511: "A pair of soft wings from a celestial dream. Their movements are so pure and delicate that they look fit to adorn the back of a heavenly being.",
    18512: "A pair of devilish wings inspired by a storm thundering across the night sky. Not only do they look impressive, they allow you to fly, too.",
    18513: "Nightbringer Edged Wings",
    18514: "A pair of wings inspired by the mighty Giga Glas Ghaibhleann, encountered in Crom Bas. You can feel tremendous power bristling from every inch of their considerable span.",
    18515: "Irusan Support Puppet",
    18516: "Secret Forest Wildflower Two-handed Sword",
    18517: "A two-handed sword inexplicably made up of beautiful wildflowers plucked from the fertile soil of a mysterious glade. Your foes will surely agree that this is the most pleasant-smelling beating they've received. (Not tradable)",
    18518: "Striped Inflatable Life Raft",
    18519: "A striped inflatable life raft that can be rowed through the water. It's light, compact, and durable. It's a good idea to keep one around for safety.",
    18520: "Inflatable Life Raft with Insignia",
    18521: "An inflatable life raft, marked with an insignia, that can be rowed through the water. It's light, compact, and durable. It's a good idea to keep one around for safety.",
    18522: "Lesser Panda Tail",
    18523: "Bird of Fortune Tail",
    18524: "Eternal Resistance Two-Handed Sword",
    18525: "Eternal Resistance Knuckles",
    18526: "A two-handed sword crafted with the latest developments in bio-alloys. This sword is strong enough to slice through any metal plating. It transforms when you enter combat mode.",
    18527: "A pair of knuckles crafted with the latest developments in bio-alloys. These knuckles will allow you to go toe-to-toe with robots of any size, armed with just your fists. They transform when you enter combat mode.",
    18528: "Mythril Lance Heavy Helm (M)",
    18529: "Mythril Lance Heavy Helm (F)",
    18530: "Royal Diamond Leather Light Helm",
    18531: "Folamh's Staff",
    18532: "A staff that Folamh uses. It is said that he summoned it with magic to compliment the aura of his outfit.",
    18533: "A cute seashell plushie inspired by the charm of coral reef dwellers. Hugging it fills both hands with plush joy.",
    18534: "A cute beluga plushie inspired by the majesty of open ocean dwellers. Hugging it fills both hands with plush joy.",
    18535: "A cute dumbo octopus plushie inspired by the mystery of deep sea dwellers. Hugging it fills both hands with plush joy.",
    18536: "Large Flamingo Inner Tube",
    18537: "Large Rainbow Inner Tube",
    18538: "A large inner tube shaped like a flamingo. Perfect for a relaxing day at the beach.",
    18539: "A large inner tube decorated like a rainbow. Perfect for a relaxing day at the beach.",
    18540: "Super Fluffy Cat Tail (1 Year)",
    18541: "A brooch that layers a large ribbon beneath a smaller ribbon, worn on the back of the waist. Its trails flutter lightly as you move.",
    18542: "펄 오이스터 쿠션",
    18543: "깊은 바닷속 신비로움을 간직한 귀여운 펄 오이스터 쿠션. 양손 가득 안기는 귀여운 쿠션이 매력적이다.",
    18544: "Eternal Resistance Bow",
    18545: "A pair of boots worn by the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next. They impart a certain quiet gravity to the wearer's footfalls.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
