    19095: "A set of specialized tools to repair Moonlight Island production equipment. Using them will restore the production capacity of Moonlight Island by 40.",
    19096: "A set of specialized tools to repair Moonlight Island production equipment. Using them will restore the production capacity of Moonlight Island by 150.",
    19097: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders to improve the island. Using it raises the satisfaction of all Moonlight Islanders by 10.",
    19098: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders to put more pep in their step. Using it restores a Moonlight Islander's endurance by 10.",
    19099: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders for the benefit of your furry friends. Using it boosts the physical attack of your summoned pet for 30 minutes. Please note that the time continues even when the pet is not summoned.",
    19100: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders for the benefit of your furry friends. Using it boosts the defense, protection, magic defense, and magic protection of your summoned pet for 30 minutes. Please note that the time continues even when the pet is not summoned.",
    19101: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders for the benefit of your furry friends. Using it boosts the physical attack, defense, protection, magic defense, and magic protection of your summoned pet for 30 minutes. Please note that the time continues even when the pet is not summoned.",
    19102: "A potion brewed by Moonlight Islanders to keep you warm in any storm. Using it prevents you from getting the Frozen effect for 10 minutes. Please note that it does not prevent any damage.",
