    40001: "Dark Moon Chain Blade",
    40002: "Wooden Blade",
    40003: "A shuriken with a mysterious quality, like the essence of the waning moon. The refined metallic ornamentation on its moon-shaped silhouette captures the eye.",
    40004: "@Lute",
    40005: "A defensive Cylinder with a mysterious quality, like the essence of the waning moon. The refined metallic ornamentation on its moon-shaped silhouette captures the eye. It specializes in defending against magic attacks. Without a cylinder, some of your Alchemy skills will be limited.",
    40006: "Special Piran Clothes (F)",
    40007: "Nightbringer Pure Wings",
    40008: "레트로 전설의 태양과 달의 검",
    40009: "레트로 전설의 대양과 담의 검",
    40010: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 검.\n마치 태양과 달의 검처럼 생겼다.(개조 불가 / 모션 카드 적용 불가 / 정령 불가)",
    40011: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 검.\n얼핏 보면 태양과 달의 검처럼 보이지만, 성능은 전혀 다르다. (수리 불가 / 개조 불가 / 모션 카드 적용 불가 / 외형 주문서 사용 불가 / 염색 불가 / 정령 불가)",
    40012: "A pair of wings imbued with the gentle light of the distant stars. Their twinkling light seems to float just above their surface, giving them an ethereal feel.",
    40013: "A pair of wings imbued with the gentle light of the distant stars. Their twinkling light seems to float just above their surface, giving them an ethereal feel.",
    40014: "레트로 전설의 태양과 달의 검",
    40015: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 검.\n마치 태양과 달의 검처럼 생겼다.",
    40016: "레트로 전설의 망치",
    40017: "@Mandolin",
    40018: "@Ukulele",
    40019: "레트로 전설의 지팡이",
    40020: "레트로 전설의 방패",
    40021: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 활.\n화려한 겉모습에 어울리는 성능을 가졌다.",
    40022: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 지팡이.\n3속성의 모든 마법을 사용할 수 있으며 중급 마법을 사용하기 위해 특별히 속성을 모을 필요도 없다.\n지팡이를 손에 쥐면 몸의 마나와 공명하게 되어 달리면서도 메디테이션을 할 수 있다.",
    40023: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 방패.\n경갑옷에서 중갑옷까지 유용하게 사용할 수 있다.",
    40024: "Bleugenne Cosmetics Piano",
    40025: "Bleugenne Cosmetics Harp",
    40026: "Bleugenne Cosmetics Mandolin",
    40027: "A piano designed in collaboration with BLEUGENNE by Bleugenne Cosmetics. Lavishly decorated with flowers and a real working fountain. The piano has a lovely, colorful tone, and melodies played on it are enhanced by the subtle sounds of the fountain. Listeners cannot help but feel reinvigorated when they hear its music.\nRight-click and press Use to place or remove the piano.",
    40028: "A harp designed in collaboration with BLEUGENNE by Bleugenne Cosmetics. An interview with the designer revealed that the wings and the branches are meant to symbolize the melody reaching from the earth to the heavens. With a clear, pure tone, listeners cannot help but feel relaxed when they hear its music.\nRight-click and press Use to place or remove the harp.",
    40029: "A mandolin designed in collaboration with BLEUGENNE by Bleugenne Cosmetics. Lavishly decorated with gems and filigree, this mandolin reintroduces classic elegance to a classic instrument. With a lively, energetic tone, listeners cannot help but want to dance when they hear its music.",
    40030: "Midnight Investigator Sword",
    40031: "Midnight Investigator Cylinder",
    40032: "Midnight Investigator Staff",
    40033: "Midnight Investigator Knuckle",
    40034: "Midnight Investigator Guard Cylinder",
    40035: "A one-handed sword issued to an investigator for the underworld. The intricate inlay and feather detailing evoke the depths of night.",
    40036: "A cylinder issued to an investigator for the underworld. The intricate inlay and feather detailing evoke the depths of night.",
    40037: "A staff issued to an investigator for the underworld. The celestial decorations and feather detailing evoke the depths of night.",
    40038: "@Lightning Wand",
    40039: "@Ice Wand",
    40040: "@Fire Wand",
    40041: "Combat Wand",
    40042: "A fishing rod imbued with the heat and power of a blazing star. You'd think that it would roast your fish for you, but alas, you still have to cook them. This fishing rod is better at catching items than fish, so the chance of catching a fish or a scroll is the same as usual, but the chance of catching an item is doubled. Your Fishing Skill must be at least Rank 5 to use it.\nTo fish, you must also equip a bait tin.",
    40043: "Noble Oblivion Kaiser Cape",
    40044: "Imperial Knight Short Blade",
    40045: "Imperial Knight Rapier",
    40046: "Imperial Knight Long Blade",
    40047: "Imperial Knight Staff",
    40048: "Whistle",
    40049: "Flute",
    40050: "Chalumeau",
    40051: "A staff issued to only the most honorable and trusted knights. The decorations contain symbols of strength and duty.",
    40052: "Raving Rabbit Crossbow",
    40053: "Raving Rabbit Shuriken",
    40054: "Raving Rabbit Chain Blade",
    40055: "A crossbow designed by members of the Raving Rabbit crew. Those who underestimate it because of the cute rabbit motif will be all the more surprised at the power it's packing.",
    40056: "A shuriken designed by members of the Raving Rabbit crew. The rabbit flourishes may give it a whimsical appearance, but it's still capable of carnage in the right hands.",
    40057: "A chain blade designed by members of the Raving Rabbit crew. The rabbit-ear design makes it somehow even more spiky--excellent for putting the hurt on enemies.",
    40058: "Candy Cane Wand",
    40059: "A sweet and jolly wand that looks like a candy cane. When you use it, your magic may smell like peppermint.",
    40060: "글래시 트리밍 레이피어",
    40061: "유리 가시와 같이 날카로움을 가지고 있는 레이피어. 크리스탈과 값비싼 보석으로 된 장식이 돋보인다.",
    40062: "Carrot Pillow",
    40063: "A cute pillow that looks like a healthy orange carrot. Hugging it fills both hands with plush joy.",
    40064: "A halo whose pattern represents the National Prestige Academy. Embrace the time-honored traditions of the National Academy.",
    40065: "Bodacious Party Facial Bandage (Facewear)",
    40066: "Bodacious Party Sunglasses (Facewear)",
    40067: "Bodacious Party Rainbow Headband",
