    40076: "Music Bottle 'F'",
    40077: "Music Bottle 'G'",
    40078: "A designer backpack in the shape of a teddy bear's head. Useful for bear-ing any load in style. When you wear it, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
    40079: "A designer backpack in the shape of a teddy bear's head. Useful for bear-ing any load in style. When you wear it, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
    40080: "A designer backpack in the shape of a teddy bear's head. Useful for bear-ing any load in style. When you wear it, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
    40081: "A designer backpack in the shape of a teddy bear's head. Useful for bear-ing any load in style. When you wear it, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
    40082: "A designer backpack in the shape of a teddy bear's head. Useful for bear-ing any load in style. When you wear it, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
