    40227: "Dittes Sacred Wand",
    40228: "Primeval Spirit Stone (Level 100)",
    40229: "A powerful Spirit Stone that gently pulses with the unbounded energy of an era before the beginning of recorded history. When used, it raises a Spirit's level to 40, but cannot be used on Spirits whose level is higher than 40. The growth catalyzed through this Spirit Stone does not affect the Spirit Bond Bonus or weekly EXP obtainment cap.",
    40230: "A powerful Spirit Stone that gently pulses with the unbounded energy of an era before the beginning of recorded history. When used, it raises a Spirit's level to 80, but cannot be used on Spirits whose level is lower than 40 or higher than 80. The growth catalyzed through this Spirit Stone does not affect the Spirit Bond Bonus or weekly EXP obtainment cap.",
