    40502: "The perfect hat to shield your eyes as you lounge under the summer sun. The cool geometric designs add to the hat's charm.",
    40503: "The perfect hat to shield your face as you lounge under the summer sun. Lace and flowers add to the hat's charm.",
    40504: "A classy swimsuit and accessories, perfect to keep you feeling cool and looking hot under the summer sun. Whether you want to jump into the waves or lounge by the shore, you'll be ready for anything. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    40505: "A classy swimsuit and accessories, perfect to keep you feeling cool and looking hot under the summer sun. Whether you want to jump into the waves or lounge by the shore, you'll be ready for anything. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
