    40522: "히트 비트 드래곤 꼬리",
    40523: "See-Through Short Hair",
    40524: "Special Royal Society Field Outfit (F)",
    40525: "A hairclip that allows one to add a ponytail styled to resemble those worn by blademasters whose weapons are keen enough to break any bonds, even those of life and death. The silver hair ornament conceals a charm to lay the dead to rest.",
    40526: "Wonderland Gentlerabbit Top Hat",
