    40907: "Blooming Romance Toy Hammer",
    40908: "A hammer decorated with romantic flowers and ribbons. Despite being intended as a toy, it can unleash great destructive force if wielded correctly. Its sweet look will have your friends heart-eyed, and your enemies seeing stars.",
