    40910: "Wandering Troupe Lute",
    40911: "Wandering Troupe Electric Guitar",
    40912: "Wandering Troupe Violin",
    40913: "Wandering Troupe Mandolin",
    40914: "An ancient, advanced flying support puppet modeled after Tina, allowing you to enjoy her bubbly energy in a compact, travel-sized form. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which orb will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    40915: "Raving Rabbit Boots (F) (Tolly's Fashion)",
    40916: "Dark Moon Shoes (M) (Tolly's Fashion)",
    40917: "This outfit is made with a high-tech material that helps you stay hidden in shadows and reduces rustling. It's designed to provide you with maximum freedom of movement and has many hidden pockets to store your gear for top-secret missions. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    40918: "Special Moonshadow Emissary's Outfit (F) (Rental)",
    40919: "High Bun Hairclip",
    40920: "Twin Heart Hairclips",
    40921: "Taise's outfit, perfect for roaming through grassy fields in search of herbs. The bag slung around her waist holds all the essentials for both exploration and extermination.",
    40922: "Only those who have surpassed limitations to awaken a mighty offensive power can utilize this light armor to its full potential. The reinforced Geas in this item enhances your Techniques.",
    40923: "Only those who have surpassed limitations to awaken a mighty offensive power can utilize these boots to their full potential. Reinforce the Geas in this item to unleash an even stronger power!",
    40924: "A Beauty Coupon that allows you to change your eyes for free in the Dressing Room under Appearance Change.",
