    40929: "Special Abyss Dragon Armor (M)",
    40930: "Special Abyss Dragon Armor (F)",
    40931: "An imposing pair of horns. The tips glow with a pale light.",
    40932: "An imposing pair of horns with a spiked crown to match. The tips glow with a pale light.",
    40933: "An imposing full breastplate fashioned from Abyss Dragon scales. Built for maximum coverage, it provides excellent defense. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    40934: "Iolar's Gauntlets (F)",
    40935: "Iolar's Greaves (M)",
    40936: "Wonderland Alice Ringband (F)",
    40937: "An outfit worn by bards who travel the countryside singing of adventure and romance. With its airy fabric and gold accents, it strikes the perfect balance between easygoing charm and distinguished refinement. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose, and applies a special change to Battlefield Overture's effect.",
