    50026: "An outfit with the deep scent of blossoming fruit.",
    50027: "An elegant outfit for idol singers, designed with dazzling ornamentation inspired by fancy dress uniforms. Its shimmering pauldron and chains are sure to catch the lights of the stage, as well as the eyes of your adoring fans.",
    50028: "Coconut",
    50029: "Only gifted alchemists are qualified to wear this uniform. Fashioned from esoteric materials sourced from the Shadow Realm and elsewhere, it unlocks the wearer's latent alchemical potential.",
    50030: "A proper clothing version of the Hebona Robe, said to enhance the fundamental Bolt Magic spells. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater magical power.",
    50031: "An outfit much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.",
    50032: "An outfit much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.",
    50033: "A helm made to complement suits of Refined Dustin Silver Knight Armor. Its unique construction, featuring overlapping scutes, adds the necessary resilience to shield one's head from all manner of blows. The decorations trailing from the back lend the wearer a sense of poise and dignity.",
    50034: "An intense yet understated suit of heavy armor that strikes fear into the hearts of one's foes. This refined masterwork is made from a variety of valuable materials, sparing nothing to achieve excellence in both defense and mobility. Crafted using polished materials, it is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.",
