    50113: "An adorable star-shaped pillow. It's soft and comforting, and just the right size to hug with both arms.",
    50114: "Garlic",
    50115: "Dragon's Broken Sword",
    50116: "An orb that holds the echoes of an ancient dragon's power. The sense of majesty and nobility you feel when touching it could bring anyone to tears.",
    50117: "Although this sword is broken, an uncanny energy completes the blade with a deadly sting. Legend has it that the dragon that broke this sword bled a single drop of blood onto it, infusing it with the dragon's own power.",
    50118: "Bottled Water",
    50119: "Ewan's Shoe (Left) (Not to be Distributed)",
    50120: "Long ago, when Ewan was a young boy and Nari a young girl, Ewan gave Nari this shoe.",
    50121: "Butter",
    50122: "Bacon",
    50123: "Duskveil Emissary's Scythe",
    50124: "A great scythe sometimes carried by the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next. While the Moonshadow Emissaries are not held to be reapers of souls, few would dispute their effectiveness in such a role, especially when wielding such an imposing weapon.",
    50125: "A great scythe sometimes carried by the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next. While the netherworld's emissaries are not held to be reapers of souls, few would dispute their effectiveness in such a role, especially when wielding such an imposing weapon.",
    50126: "Elegant Riding Crop",
    50127: "Shrimp",
    50128: "A beautiful riding crop suitable for all equestrian pursuits. Though intended for horseback riding, getting hit with it really stings. But if you're into that...",
    50129: "An enchanted quill pen that leaves behind a flowing, luminescent script when tracing through the air. Novel yet mysterious, it's the sort of magical curio beloved by scholars and socialites alike.",
