    50162: "Kite Shield",
    50163: "A well-balanced sword capable of quick strikes. Aside from the fact that it's difficult to perform a three-hit combo with, it is an excellent all-around weapon.",
    50164: "A short bludgeon with a hefty, flanged head of tempered iron. Simple, but effective.",
    50165: "This double-bladed combat axe was created through a process more ancient than is typically used in the crafting of modern weaponry.",
    50166: "Required to hurl javelins. It is carved from a length of wood with a groove notched into one end to hold the butt of a javelin, then finished with a leather grip. Once a javelin is loaded, an overhand swing will send the projectile flying.",
    50167: "A longbow with a leather-wrapped grip that reinforces the limbs while giving the archer a secure grip on the weapon.",
    50168: "A type of bow that fires shorter bolts, using a mechanism to draw back its stiff metal limbs. Crossbows allow marksmen to focus purely on accuracy without having to worry about the force of the shot. Because of this, many have found them conducive to landing critical hits.",
    50169: "A simple Control Bar used to control Marionettes. Its straightforward, minimalist design consists of two boards crossed over each other and fastened in the middle.",
    50170: "A two-handed sword designed for powerful slashing cuts with its flexible blade. In the hands of a skilled warrior, this weapon has few equals.",
    50171: "A lance made from the wood of the sturdy conifers that grow in Iria's Physis region. It takes an entire log to make one of these massive lances, and rumor has it there's a Giant who goes out every night to hew down enough trees to continue producing lances unabated.\n\nWhile lances excel at attacking enemies at a distance, only those who have truly mastered the art of lance combat can use them at close range.",
    50172: "The trio of spikes attached to these knuckles make for a more powerful punch than a bare fist, in addition to offering additional protection for the wearer's hands. Knuckle attacks that begin with a body check flow into a tackle as soon as the opponent goes down, granting you another opportunity to attack. Knuckle damage draws on the wielder's Will.",
    50173: "A shuriken with four curved blades jutting out from the center. Though simple in shape, in the hands of a trained Ninja, it can be used to devastating effect.",
    50174: "An easy-to-handle Chain Blade designed for initiates to the art. Its design focuses on the links between the blade segments, allowing for intuitive control when extended.",
    50175: "This shield, which takes its name from the kites it supposedly resembles, is also known as a teardrop design. The length offers a measure of protection to the lower body in combat, and holding it in your off-hand helps absorb the impact of blows when you block an attack using a skill. It can be used with both light and heavy armor.",
    50176: "Lovely Pan Bag",
    50177: "Lovely Pan Scooter",
    50178: "A bag made in the shape of Pan's face. It seems perfectly suited for carrying small belongings.",
    50179: "A scooter decorated with Pan's cute face. It's a fun and convenient way to get around, and it'll pack a punch if you swing it at someone, too.",
    50180: "Zongzi Bag",
    50181: "A lotus leaf bag on which a cheerful rice dumpling has decided to hitch a ride. It seems durable enough to give enemies a good thwack, if needed--just be sure not to smoosh your innocent passenger in the process.",
