    50339: "A thousand-year-old advanced support puppet depicting a dauntless young woman working to deliver letters and parcels as an Erinn Courier. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50340: "An advanced support puppet depicting a dauntless young woman working to deliver letters and parcels as an Erinn Courier. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50341: "A thousand-year-old advanced support puppet designed to resemble Cowenna, the exemplar of the Elemental Knight Arcana, here to encourage you to train hard and eat a diet high in protein. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50342: "An advanced support puppet designed to resemble Cowenna, the exemplar of the Elemental Knight Arcana, here to encourage you to train hard and eat a diet high in protein. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50343: "A thousand-year-old advanced support puppet designed to resemble Eochaid, the exemplar of the Harmonic Saint Arcana. Not actually that much shorter than the real Eochaid, but don't tell him that. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50344: "An advanced support puppet designed to resemble Eochaid, the exemplar of the Harmonic Saint Arcana. Not actually that much shorter than the real Eochaid, but don't tell him that. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50345: "A thousand-year-old advanced support puppet designed to resemble Laoire, the perpetually busy head of the Arcana Association. May organize your loose paperwork if left unattended. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50346: "An advanced support puppet designed to resemble Laoire, the perpetually busy head of the Arcana Association. May organize your loose paperwork if left unattended. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    50347: "Irusan's Bell (Event)",
    50348: "Unfinished Reverie's Diadem Halo (Event)",
    50349: "Destructive Robe (M) (Event)",
    50350: "Destructive Robe (M) (Event)",
    50351: "Destructive Robe (F) (Event)",
    50352: "Destructive Robe (F) (Event)",
    50353: "A thin chime cast in a motif that brings to mind Irusan, whom you encountered in Crom Bas. Irusan's disarmingly cute look might be easier to appreciate if only they weren't so irritating...",
    50354: "A diadem and veil glimpsed over the head of Cailleach's Unfinished Reverie. The ancient energy that once lay heavy upon this ornament of metal and cloth has dissipated, rendering it wearable as a halo. With it floating over your head, it almost feels as though you take winter with you wherever you go.",
    50355: "A robe whose every strand is replete with a forbidden power potent enough to sunder the fabric of reality. Pairs well with the Destructive Shoes and Destructive Gloves.",
    50356: "A robe whose every strand is replete with a forbidden power potent enough to sunder the fabric of reality. Pairs well with the Destructive Shoes and Destructive Gloves.",
    50357: "This is a special Fomor Pass that Tarlach gave you. Put it on the Fiodh Dungeon altar to enter Fiodh Dungeon, where you can find the Magic Powder of Preservation.\nParty Size: 1-4",
    50358: "A pair of shoes much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, they boast improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.\n\nA message is tooled into one.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    50359: "A pair of shoes much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, they boast improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.\n\nA message is tooled into one.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    50360: "NPC Human/Elf Female Mannequin Face (Not to be Distributed)",
    50361: "NPC Giant Male Mannequin Face (Not to be Distributed)",
    50362: "A Beauty Coupon that allows you to change your eyes for free in the Dressing Room under Appearance Change.",
    50363: "NPC Human/Elf Male Mannequin Face (Not to be Distributed)",
    50364: "NPC Human/Elf Female Mannequin Face (Not to be Distributed)",
    50365: "A magic ink that imbues glyphs with a special color.\nThis color is only made in Bri Leith.",
    50366: "무등고래 호루라기(메달 불가)",
    50367: "우리들의 친구인 동물을 만날 수 있는 기회. 사랑스런 무등고래를 만나보세요. 호루라기 사용 시, 200레벨의 무등고래 펫을 획득할 수 있습니다.\n획득한 펫은 동물 캐릭터 분양 메달에 담을 수 없습니다.",
    50368: "A torch made for an important ritual. Right now, it's still unlit.",
    50369: "A mysterious blade enchanted with magical energy. Refined blades such as these can serve as a foundation for an immensely powerful weapon.\n\nProduced through Hillwen Engineering, and can be used as a crafting material.",
    50370: "A mysterious metal enchanted with magical energy. Refined alloys such as this can serve as a foundation for an immensely powerful weapon.\n\nProduced through Hillwen Engineering, and can be used as a crafting material.",
    50371: "A mysterious ore fragment enchanted with magical energy. Enriched ores such as this can serve as a foundation for an immensely powerful weapon.\n\nProduced through Hillwen Engineering, and can be used as a crafting material.",
