    2000001: "These wings express a hidden aspect of the Beast. A strong power can be felt from each and every feather.",
    2000002: "Bunny Doll Tail and Bow (1 Year)",
    2000003: "A bunny doll tail tied with an adorable bow. The design is simple but really cute.",
    2000004: "Lovely Flower Crown Halo",
    2000005: "Cethlenn's Staff",
    2000006: "로즈 템테이션 클러치 백",
    2000007: "우아한 검은 장미를 중심으로 엮은 꽃다발. 들고 다니면 우아한 아름다움을 느낄 수 있다.",
    2000008: "A cheek bandage face accessory. You can equip it along with some hat items.",
    2000009: "A drum set inspired by the sight of the sun rising over the sea. The oceanic motif shines through in the shapes of the waves, seashells, and starfish decorating its surface. If you stand on the shore at daybreak and play, your beat will resound over the crashing of the waves.",
    2000010: "A wireless microphone inspired by the sight of the sun rising over the sea. The oceanic motif shines through in the wave-shaped decoration. If you stand on the shore at daybreak and sing, your voice will resound over the crashing of the waves. Your neighbors may ask you to pipe down, but pay them no mind. Sing!",
    2000011: "A lance fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. It has been imbued with an ancient power that resounds in the clangor of its blows.",
    2000012: "꽃을 찾아 날아가야만 할 것 같은 나비 날개. 착용하면 날 수 있을 것 같다.",
    2000013: "Moonlit Wolf Tail",
    2000014: "A shuriken imbued with a transcendent power capable of setting free souls in bondage. In skilled hands, the dynamic energies coursing through it can be released to explosive effect.",
    2000016: "Captivating Enchanting Piat Wings",
    2000017: "Graceful Windcatcher Wings",
