    2020001: "A walking cane that, in the right hands, can serve as an effective weapon. After all, one never knows when a respectable social affair might erupt into a spirited fracas.",
    2020002: "A pair of rifles favored by members of the mafia for their compact size. For their slim profile, they offer strong firepower.",
    2020003: "A pair of Revolvers favored by members of the mafia for their classic profile. It's very quick to draw and fire, which is important when one shot may be all you need.",
