    2030001: "This two-handed sword was once wielded by a leader in a dark cult. The sharp blade is imbued with a mysterious invisible energy. When sheathed, the darkness appears suppressed.",
    2030002: "This lance was once wielded by a leader in a dark cult. A mysterious invisible energy circles the blade.\n\nWhile lances excel at attacking enemies at a distance, only those who have truly mastered the art of lance combat can use them at close range.",
