    2050000: "A piano used by the occultic leader of an order veiled in secrecy, graced with the figure of a goddess wearing a crown of thorns. While its refined ornamentation lends it a beautiful aesthetic, the music it makes has the power to seduce and bewitch others, enveloping their bodies and minds with a strange energy.\n\nYou can set up/remove the piano by right-clicking and selecting [Use].",
    2050001: "Moonlit Leopard Tail (1 Year)",
    2050002: "A wolf's tail. The elegant ornamentation pairs well with the soft, fluffy fur.",
    2050003: "Fallen Noble Eagle Wings",
    2050004: "Dramatic Bleugenne Fur Coat",
    2050005: "Angelic wings draped with vines replete with blossoms in full bloom. Imbued with the spirit of summer, they will remain forever beautiful.\n(Dyeable)",
    2050006: "A large, fluffy fox tail sometimes worn by maids and butlers of House Elysees eager to prove themselves foxier than the competition.",
