    2200332: "Evil Angel Fulgur Arrow",
    2200333: "Arrows imbued with pure lightning-elemental energy. Surges of electricity crackle up and down their shafts.",
    2200334: "Arrows imbued with pure lightning-elemental energy. Surges of electricity crackle up and down their shafts.",
