    2200360: "Perseus Forbidden Spell Book",
    2200361: "Perseus Tyrannus Guard Cylinder",
    2200362: "Nightbringer Vega Orb",
    2200363: "A bow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    2200364: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    2200365: "A wand crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    2200366: "A wand containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    2200367: "A shield containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    2200368: "Special arrows that, when touched, fill one with a chilling emptiness. Use them with the Nightbringer Predator Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\n\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Nightbringer Predator.",
    2200369: "Arrows containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. Use them with the Perseus Voiceless Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\n\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Perseus Voiceless Bow.",
    2200370: "A spellbook crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    2200375: "Celtic Royal Crossbow",
    2200376: "Celtic Crossbow",
    2200379: "A greataxe fashioned from a restored battle axe said to have been wielded by a goddess. Its broad, sharp double blades strike with unyielding force, inflicting great damage on foes. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.",
    2200380: "A greataxe fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Its broad, curved edge can cleave through the toughest targets. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.",
    2200381: "A staff born of the will of a goddess. Those who upgrade it will find themselves able to more effectively regulate their mana. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    2200382: "A staff that reflects the generosity of a goddess, enabling the wielder to cast powerful magic attacks or support allies with the Party Healing skill. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    2200383: "A lance fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. It has been imbued with an ancient power that resounds in the clangor of its blows.",
    2200384: "A pair of knuckles fashioned in the likeness of a pair possessed by a goddess. With thick, rigid metal plating on the outer hand and tipped with a sharp spike, they're capable of turning powerful punches into lethal blows.",
    2200385: "A pair of next-generation guns fashioned in the likeness of firearms possessed by a goddess. Based on the original Dowra SE, this model has been designed with a higher rate of fire, greater ammunition capacity, and more destructive power.",
    2200386: "A shuriken fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Spinning as it flashes through the air, its five sharpened points can slice enemies to ribbons.",
    2200387: "Born from ancient Celtic legends, this mighty weapon embodies both nature's generosity and wrath. The moment it touches your hand, a powerful vibration surges through it--as if responding to your very will.",
    2200388: "Morrighan's Regalia (F)",
    2200389: "A staff whose design takes inspiration from the rows of hanging lanterns that illuminate thoroughfares and pathways during festivals. Carrying it, you feel as though you could lead a mysterious procession.",
