    2200558: "Wings that hold the power to tempt all, even unto their eternal rest. They fold during combat, but otherwise stretch out in all their magnificence.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200559: "Large wings with feathers full of light. Metal ornaments adorn it, as if symbolizing the sun.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200560: "Lavish feathered wings that shine brilliantly. The scattered light around the wings gives them a beautiful aura.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200561: "Wings that grace a saint blessed by angels, tasked with guiding and protecting the world in accordance with the will of the light. It is said that those who feel the wind from the beating of these wings will have their strength renewed.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200562: "A sheer bolt of silken fabric like those that adorn immortal beings in celestial dreams. Its fluttering movements are so graceful, so subtle, that it truly looks the part of a heavenly garment.",
    2200563: "Airy wings that undulate gently in even the slightest of breezes. Their ethereal ambiance often draws curious onlookers.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200564: "Wings filled with holy light. Their soft flapping feels like a divine embrace.\n(Dyeable)",
    2200565: "Wings that spread as wide as the sky. Don't be surprised if they actually do carry you into the grand horizon.\n(Dyeable)",
