    2220018: "Special Saint Guardian's Full Armor (F)",
    2230004: "Nightbringer Pure Wings",
    2230005: "레트로 전설의 태양과 달의 검",
    2230006: "레트로 전설의 대양과 담의 검",
    2230007: "도트 그래픽이 돋보이는 전설의 검.\n마치 태양과 달의 검처럼 생겼다.(개조 불가 / 모션 카드 적용 불가 / 정령 불가)",
    2230008: "Wizard Robe Support Armor (M)",
    2230009: "Wizard Robe Support Armor (F)",
    2230010: "Elemental Harmony Earring (Facewear)",
    2230011: "For Jousting Tournament Cutscene",
    2230012: "@Refined Northern Lights Armor (M)",
    2230013: "@Refined Northern Lights Armor (F)",
    2230014: "Elegant Downy Feather Wings",
    2230015: "Wings made of mystical downy feathers. They have a warmth and comfort that seem to envelop one's body.",
    2230016: "Ceann Bliana Skirmisher's Cuirass (M)",
    2230017: "Ceann Bliana Skirmisher's Cuirass (F)",
    2230018: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (M)",
    2230019: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (M) (Rental)",
    2230020: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (M)",
    2230021: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (F)",
    2230022: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (F) (Rental)",
    2230023: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (F)",
    2230024: "Refined Northern Lights Armor (M) (Rental)",
    2230025: "Refined Northern Lights Armor (F) (Rental)",
    2230026: "Refined Northern Lights Armor (M)",
    2230027: "Refined Northern Lights Armor (F)",
