    2230034: "Refined Majestic Knight Armor (M)",
    2230035: "Refined Majestic Knight Armor (F)",
    2230036: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (M)",
    2230037: "Refined Languhiris Chaser Armor (F)",
    2230038: "Ultimate Geas Devastation Chestplate (M)",
    2230039: "Ultimate Geas Devastation Chestplate (F)",
    2230040: "Geas Devastation Chestplate (M) (Event)",
    2230041: "Geas Devastation Chestplate (F) (Event)",
    2230042: "Ultimate Geas Devastation Chestplate (M) (Event)",
