    2400172: "A fine coat tailored for the noble house of Berchel, showcasing the family's elegance and savoir-faire. It looks just as nice hanging off the shoulders as it does buttoned up.",
    2400173: "도깨비 불을 형상화 한 날개, 도깨비 불이 태우지 못할 것은 없다.",
