    2400178: "Oblivion Kaiser Scythe",
    2400179: "Forbidden Tome",
    2400180: "A scythe said to have once been wielded by a legendary lord of the abyss, in whose hands each sweep of its serrated blade was said to shriek like a maddening wind.",
    2400181: "A tome long sealed away, said to hold part of a destructive spell powerful enough to bring about the end of the world.",
    2400182: "Oblivion Kaiser Halberd",
    2400183: "A polearm said to have once been wielded by a legendary lord of the abyss. The aura of emptiness that trails its blade bears the tingling chill of the void. Ancient scrolls warn that any soul pierced by it will be consigned to eternal oblivion.",
    2400184: "Wonderland Wand of Clubs",
    2400185: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    2400186: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nThere's a message engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids your journey across Erinn.</color>",
    2400187: "Primitive Stone Axe (Axe)",
    2400188: "An axe crafted by knapping flint to a razor's edge, then binding it to a sturdy shaft with all-natural materials gathered in the forest. When you hold it, you can feel the raw energy of nature pulsing in your hand.",
    2400189: "Fergseus Dynamic Crossbow",
    2400190: "A crossbow that has withstood Ferghus's zealous hammering. If anything seems off, it's probably just your imagination.\n\nA small engraving, legible only upon close inspection, reads, \"Carpentry ain't exactly my forte, but if you need any work done on this, come on over and I'll get you sorted out.</color>\"",
    2400191: "A halo depicting a shining chariot that draws the sun behind it on its journey across the sky.",
    2400192: "A halo depicting a gleaming chariot that draws the moon behind it on its journey across the sky.",
    2400193: "An advanced support puppet based on the idea of a whimsical rabbit who lives among the stars. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    2400194: "A thousand-year-old advanced support puppet based on the idea of a whimsical panda who lives among the stars. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
