    2400219: "Wings flush with smooth, beautiful feathers. They possess a delicate, heavenly grace.",
    2400220: "A pair of soft, downy wings that lets you fly amongst the sweetest dreams.\n(Dyeable)",
    2400221: "A pair of mecha wings equipped with fusion thrusters for speed and nano-engines for maneuverability. Whether you're traveling in atmo or out, you'll be able to fly high. This special compact version has no decrease in performance.\n(Dyeable)",
    2400222: "Wings that symbolize the Saint Guardian, made from a multitude of razor-edged blades. Their grandeur is bound to impress all those who look upon them.\n(Dyeable)",
