    3100002: "Destroyer's Blade",
    3100003: "A shuriken with a mysterious quality, like the essence of the waning moon. The refined metallic ornamentation on its moon-shaped silhouette captures the eye.",
    3100004: "Revolutionary Resistance Gatling Guns",
    3100005: "A replica of the sniper rifle of a legendary resistance fighter who never gives in to tyranny. Since it's a replica, it can't actually fire bullets, but it packs a punch if you swing it at someone.",
    3100006: "Engagement Ring",
    3100007: "Engagement Ring",
    3100008: "Eternal Fulgur Arrow",
    3100009: "Arrows imbued with pure lightning-elemental energy. Surges of electricity crackle up and down their shafts.",
