    3120001: "Nightbringer Wraith Chain Blade",
    3120003: "An orb that holds the echoes of an ancient dragon's power. The sense of majesty and nobility you feel when touching it could bring anyone to tears.",
    3120004: "A two-handed hammer fashioned from a restored hammer said to have been wielded by a goddess in judgment of her foes. Despite its hulking size and the destructive power of which it is capable, both humans and Elves can wield it with ease.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3120005: "A two-handed axe fashioned from a restored great axe said to have been wielded by a goddess. Its broad, sharp double blades strike with unyielding force, inflicting great damage on foes. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3120006: "A two-handed axe fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Its broad, curved edge can cleave through the toughest targets. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3120007: "Claimh Solas",
