    3120026: "Celtic Clashing Lance (Rental)",
    3120027: "A bow fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Great strength is needed to draw it, but each arrow loosed is driven by that same potent force.\n\n(Cannot be dyed, enchanted, reforged, upgraded, gifted to a partner, made into a Spirit Weapon, have its enchants extracted, or receive the effect of a Trade Unlock Potion.)",
    3120028: "A two-handed sword fashioned in the likeness of one wielded by a goddess. Imbued with the power of an outstanding swordsman, its keen edge can cleave through foes.\n\n(Cannot be dyed, enchanted, reforged, upgraded, gifted to a partner, made into a Spirit Weapon, have its enchants extracted, or receive the effect of a Trade Unlock Potion.)",
    3120029: "A lance fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. It has been imbued with an ancient power that resounds in the clangor of its blows.\n\n(Cannot be dyed, enchanted, reforged, upgraded, gifted to a partner, made into a Spirit Weapon, have its enchants extracted, or receive the effect of a Trade Unlock Potion.)",
    3120030: "Talvish Balloon (5 uses) (Not tradable)",
