    3120037: "Reichel Prevail Control Bar",
    3120038: "Berchel Prevail Kriegsmesser",
    3120039: "Reichel Prevail Kriegsmesser",
    3120040: "Berchel Prevail Blossombough",
    3120041: "Reichel Prevail Blossombough",
    3120042: "A bouquet of cottonwood twigs that serves as a spellcasting implement, crafted for the noble house of Berchel. Rustic yet fluffy, it showcases the family's elegance and savoir-faire.",
    3120043: "A bouquet of cottonwood twigs that serves as a spellcasting implement, crafted for the noble house of Reichel. Rustic yet fluffy, it showcases the family's dignity and erudition.",
    3120044: "A set of Control Bars fashioned of aged hardwood and polished brass for the noble house of Berchel. Said to be used in extravagant theatrical productions, they showcase the family's elegance and savoir-faire.",
    3120045: "A set of Control Bars fashioned of aged hardwood and polished brass for the noble house of Reichel. Said to be used in extravagant theatrical productions even grander than those of House Berchel, they showcase the family's dignity and erudition.",
    3120046: "An impressive \"war knife\" large enough to cleave a horse and rider in twain, presuming one has the strength to swing it. Forged at the behest of the noble house of Berchel, it showcases the family's elegance and savoir-faire.",
    3120047: "An impressive \"war knife\" large enough to cleave a horse and rider in twain, presuming one has the strength to swing it. Forged at the behest of the noble house of Reichel, it showcases the family's dignity and erudition.",
    3120048: "A staff fashioned in the druidic tradition from a flowering branch, commissioned by the noble house of Berchel. Endowed with an enchantment said to keep its owner \"light on their feet,\" it showcases the family's elegance and savoir-faire.",
    3120049: "A staff fashioned in the druidic tradition from a flowering branch, commissioned by the noble house of Reichel. Endowed with an enchantment said to keep its owner \"light on their feet,\" it showcases the family's dignity and erudition.",
    3120050: "Elegant Romantic Lace Umbrella",
    3120051: "Charming Romantic Lace Umbrella",
    3120052: "A delicate lace umbrella, perfect for sharing with your special someone. The luxurious lace details elevate any look.",
