    3140000: "Dual Guns of Blossoming Memories",
    3140001: "Shuriken of Blossoming Memories",
    3140002: "Lightning Bow",
    3140003: "A two-handed sword infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning.",
    3140004: "A bow infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning.",
    3140005: "Daring Duckling Crossbow",
    3140006: "Daring Duckling Banana Dual Gun",
    3140007: "Not just any crossbow, this one includes a chubby duckling wearing a cute hat--mainly for moral support, but it may be concealing a few extra bolts just for you. The cloud pattern and the inner tube decoration put it in the running for the most relaxing crossbow you'll ever take into battle.",
    3140008: "This Messenger Bag is made out of steel-infused fibers, making it resistant to all kinds of dangers. It will keep your most important equipment safe on a top-secret mission.",
    3140009: "Sly Serpent Cane",
    3140010: "Sly Serpent Chalice",
    3140011: "Sly Serpent Clutch",
    3140012: "A cane for those who know that beauty and deadliness are two sides of a coin. Topped with a fearsome gold cobra's head, it projects an aura of unapproachability.",
    3140013: "A chalice for those who know that beauty and deadliness are two sides of a coin. Take a sip; the venom within cannot touch one with the spirit of a viper.",
    3140014: "A clutch for those who know that beauty and deadliness are two sides of a coin. Any schemes contained within are safe behind snakeskin.",
    3140015: "향기로운 꽃송이",
    3140016: "아일린을 만난 계절의 꽃. 따스한 아일린의 미소가 떠오르는 분홍빛 벚꽃이다. 아일린을 만났던 계절의 기억을 떠올릴 수 있을 것 같다.",
    3140017: "Ancient Nine-Tailed Fox Support Puppet",
    3140018: "Ancient Morrighan Support Puppet",
    3140019: "Ancient Neamhain Support Puppet",
    3140020: "Ancient Cichol Support Puppet",
    3140021: "Ancient Macha Support Puppet",
    3140022: "Ancient Belisha Support Puppet",
    3140023: "Queen of Hearts Staff",
    3140024: "Irusan Support Puppet",
    3140025: "Secret Forest Wildflower Two-handed Sword",
    3140026: "A pair of dual guns crafted with the latest developments in bio-alloys. The unique firing mechanism allows these guns to be used even in the vacuum of space. They transform when you enter combat mode.",
    3140027: "A pair of knuckles fashioned in the likeness of a pair possessed by a goddess. With thick, rigid metal plating on the outer hand and tipped with a sharp spike, they're capable of turning powerful punches into lethal blows.\n<color=1>These weapons have been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3140028: "Celtic Throwing Star",
    3140029: "A shuriken fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Spinning as it flashes through the air, its five sharpened points can slice enemies to ribbons.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3140030: "Celtic Tetra Cylinder",
    3140031: "A cylinder fashioned in the likeness of a similar implement possessed by a goddess. It greatly enhances the effects of elemental Alchemy skills.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    3140032: "Celtic Tribolt Wand",
    3140054: "Summer Casual Sports Bag",
    3140055: "At times, circumstances may call for quick and courageous action in defense of another. It is Iolar's belief that, in such critical moments, the merciful voice of Lymilark will serve as her guide.\n\n<color=1>\"Call unto me, and I will answer, revealing unto thee great and secret things, which thou knowest not.\"</color>",
    3140056: "Of all Lymilark's teachings, it is the emphasis on a heart attuned to loving and protecting others that most inspires Iolar. Day after day, she raises her shield that others may be spared from harm, spreading the teachings of Lymilark in word and in deed.\n\n<color=1>\"For I am not ashamed of the gospel, for it is the power of Lymilark to sustain all who believe.\"</color>",
    3140057: "Soul Liberator Orb",
    3140058: "Red Heart Glow Wand",
    3140059: "Pink Heart Glow Wand",
    3140060: "Yellow Heart Glow Wand",
