    3160004: "Bright Conch Shell",
    3160005: "A chinchilla doll wearing a Marine outfit. Getting hit with this might not hurt your body, but your pride may never recover.",
    3160006: "A beautiful conch shell glimmering with all sorts of colors. You can almost hear the crashing of the waves if you hold it up to your ear. It glimmers brilliantly in the night.",
    3160007: "A sumptuously decorated party masque used by the Queen to conceal her true identity at masquerade balls and costume parties. Whether you will find such success depends in part on your acting ability.",
    3160008: "Lovely Flower Crown Halo",
    3160009: "Sweet Flower Crown Halo",
