    3200000: "Nightbringer Rogue Crossbow (Event)",
    3200001: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow (Event)",
    3200002: "A lance crafted to resemble a spider. Like any deadly arachnid, its small size hides its destructive power.\n\nWhile lances excel at attacking enemies at a distance, only those who have truly mastered the art of lance combat can use them at close range.",
    3200003: "A chain blade that draws inspiration from a spider. Its chain entangles foes like a web, then slices them with its razor-sharp blades.",
    3200004: "Novice Dungeoneer Support Chain Blade",
    3200005: "Beginner Dungeoneer Support Chain Blade",
    3200006: "Intermediate Dungeoneer Support Chain Blade",
    3200007: "Advanced Dungeoneer Support Chain Blade",
    3200008: "A Chain Blade modified for novices. The complexly shaped blade has increased attack damage.\n(Works with the Upgrade Stone sold at the Dungeon Guide Shop.)\n(Not eligible for Enchant Burning.)\n(Not tradable.)",
    3200009: "A Chain Blade modified for beginners. The complexly shaped blade has increased attack damage.\n(Works with the Upgrade Stone sold at the Dungeon Guide Shop.)\n(Not eligible for Enchant Burning.)\n(Not tradable.)",
    3200010: "Bunny Doll Tail and Bow (1 Year)",
    3200011: "This teddy bear stirs feelings of warmth and caring in those who hold it. It seems to welcome big hugs, and will gladly accompany you on your journeys.",
    3200012: "A well-loved teddy bear from your childhood. Though your adventures together have left it a bit threadbare in places, thinking of those heartfelt times makes its presence all the more comforting.",
    3200013: "Soul Liberator Greataxe",
    3200014: "A greataxe imbued with a transcendent power capable of setting free souls in bondage. In skilled hands, the dynamic energies coursing through it can be released to explosive effect.",
    3200015: "Moonlit Dragon Tail",
    3200016: "Moonlit Dragon Tail (1 Year)",
    3200017: "A striped inflatable life raft that can be rowed through the water. It's light, compact, and durable. It's a good idea to keep one around for safety.",
    3200018: "Inflatable Life Raft with Insignia",
    3200019: "An inflatable life raft, marked with an insignia, that can be rowed through the water. It's light, compact, and durable. It's a good idea to keep one around for safety.",
    3200020: "Lesser Panda Tail",
    3200021: "Bird of Fortune Tail",
    3200022: "Eternal Resistance Two-Handed Sword",
    3200023: "A cute dumbo octopus plushie inspired by the mystery of deep sea dwellers. Hugging it fills both hands with plush joy.",
    3200024: "Large Flamingo Inner Tube",
    3200025: "Large Rainbow Inner Tube",
    3200026: "A large inner tube shaped like a flamingo. Perfect for a relaxing day at the beach.",
    3200027: "A large inner tube decorated like a rainbow. Perfect for a relaxing day at the beach.",
    3200028: "Super Fluffy Cat Tail (1 Year)",
    3200029: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3200030: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3200031: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nThere's a message engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids your journey across Erinn.</color>",
    3200032: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    3200033: "Primitive Stone Axe (Hammer)",
    3200034: "Juicy Barbecued Meat",
    3200035: "An axe crafted by knapping flint to a razor's edge, then binding it to a sturdy shaft with all-natural materials gathered in the forest. When you hold it, you can feel the raw energy of nature pulsing in your hand.",
    3200036: "A cartoonishly large hunk of meat, grilled to perfection. Mmm...so tasty! Equipping it allows your to strike a special pose.",
    3200037: "Wanderer's Pipe Greatsword",
    3200038: "A smoking pipe greatsword carried by one who crosses freely over the borders of life and death. In its smoke, the demise of many enemies has been foretold.",
    3200039: "Rakshasa Pipe Greatsword",
    3200040: "A smoking pipe greatsword carried by one who crosses freely over the borders of life and death. In its smoke, the demise of many enemies has been foretold.",
    3200041: "Dazzling Debut Leopard Tail",
