    3400000: "Legendary Pixel Bow",
    3400001: "A tube that lets you ride out even high waves in tasty, sugary comfort. It's been imbued with magic so you can even ride it on land!",
    3400002: "A tube that lets you ride out even high waves in tasty, sugary comfort. It's been imbued with magic so you can even ride it on land!",
    3400003: "Demolition Breaker Arrows",
    3400004: "A large teddy bear that's totally hip with it. Or so it thinks, with its head full of neon fluff. When you take it with you on your adventures, you feel as though you're sliding through a candy-colored dreamscape.",
    3400005: "Lightning Staff",
    3400006: "The staff that Eochaid usually carries with him, capable of casting all three types of elemental magic. It greatly amplifies the wielder's magical power by accumulating the residual mana left from all the spells cast by its bearer.",
    3400007: "Moonlit Wolf Tail",
    3400008: "Moonlit Wolf Tail (1 Year)",
    3400009: "Moonlit Puffy Cat Tail",
    3400010: "Moonlit Puffy Cat Tail (1 Year)",
    3400011: "Moonlit Whale Tail",
    3400012: "Moonlit Whale Tail (1 Year)",
    3400013: "Moonlit Leopard Tail",
    3400014: "Moonlit Leopard Tail (1 Year)",
    3400015: "Intermediate Dungeoneer Support Chain Blade",
    3400016: "White Music Note Glow Wand",
    3400017: "Ethereal Angel Long Bow",
    3400018: "Ethereal Devil Scythe",
    3400019: "A long bow made for the performance of a great celestial dance. With the brightness of its divine power, you could light up new stars in the firmament.",
    3400020: "A scythe made for the performance of a great celestial dance. With the darkness of its divine power, you could strike down every star in the firmament.",
    3400021: "로얄 소사이어티 사이드",
    3400022: "로얄 소사이어티 대낫 양손 도끼",
    3400023: "왕립학회에서 포션을 활용하여 강화시킨 대형 낫. 밤에 빛나는 포션이 칼날까지 흐르며, 아름다움을 더해준다.",
    3400024: "왕립학회에서 포션을 활용하여 강화시킨 대형 도끼 낫. 밤에 빛나는 포션이 칼날까지 흐르며, 아름다움을 더해준다.",
    3400025: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3400026: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3400028: "A bow that has that has withstood Ferghus's zealous hammering. If anything seems off, it's probably just your imagination.\n\nA small engraving, legible only upon close inspection, reads, \"<color=1>I'm no carpenter, but I think it came out pretty nice, all things considered! Wood'll yield to a hammer as sure as iron.</color>\"",
    3400029: "Magical Frog Robe",
    3400030: "칠석 기념 헤보나 로브",
    3400031: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3400032: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3400036: "Void Robe (M)",
    3400037: "Void Robe (F)",
    3400038: "Abyssal Robe (M)",
    3400039: "Abyssal Robe (F)",
