    3400041: "Destructive Robe (F) (Event)",
    3400042: "Void Robe (M)",
    3400043: "Void Robe (F)",
    3500000: "A legendary staff crafted with care from only the finest quality pixels. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    3500001: "A legendary shield crafted with care from only the finest quality pixels.\nIn spite of its graphics, it's versatile enough to be used with both Light Armor and Heavy Armor setups.",
    3500002: "Soldier's Field Shovel",
    3500003: "Soldier's Gear Bag",
    3500004: "Soldier's Field Axe",
    3500005: "Soldier's Automatic Pistol",
    3500006: "Crow Knuckle",
    3500007: "A knuckle that feels remarkably light. Crafted from an enchanted feather, it holds potent destructive force despite its unnaturally light heft.",
    3500008: "Adventurer's Fluted Short Sword",
    3500009: "A small, lightweight weapon that is great for quick attacks. It allows you to be agile during combat, and also has high ATT. (Cannot be upgraded, reforged, or enchanted)",
    3500010: "Legendary Pixel Sawloona Blade",
    3500011: "A legendary blade crafted with care from only the finest quality pixels.\nAt first glance, it would appear to resemble a real Soluna Blade, but...a few swings is all it will take to discover the difference. (Cannot be repaired)",
    3500012: "Secret Garden Bottle",
    3500014: "Steam-Powered Spark Staff",
    3500015: "Twin Moons Replica Hammer",
    3500016: "Fountain Pen Lance",
    3500017: "A satchel favored by a certain historian. The various documents and scrolls scattered in the bag as well as the watch hanging from it leave quite the impression.",
    3500018: "A two-handed sword in the shape of a quill pen. The feather-like blade is surprisingly sharp.",
    3500019: "A hammer made to look like a replica modeled off of Eweca and Ladeca.",
    3500020: "A lance made to look like a giant fountain pen. The sharpness of the nib strikes fear into the hearts of enemies.",
    3500023: "Etain Staff",
    3500026: "Decent Treasure Hunt L-Rod (Event)",
    3500029: "Flora Lantern",
    3500030: "Hexagon Lantern",
    3500031: "Chick Lantern",
    3500032: "A simple yet elegant glass candlestick.",
    3500033: "A beautifully luminous flower-themed lantern.",
    3500034: "A six-sided lantern made in an appealing Eastern style.",
    3500035: "A lantern fashioned in the form of a cute chick.",
    3500036: "Black Rose Bouquet",
    3500037: "A staff decorated with the design of black roses. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    3500038: "A wheeled contraption designed to move large amounts of food at once. The sweet scent of fruit and dessert wafts from the tray.",
    3500039: "A bouquet of elegant black roses. Just carrying it around makes you feel like the epitome of dignified beauty.",
    3500040: "A Chain Blade modified for intermediate players. The complexly shaped blade has increased attack damage.\n(Works with the Upgrade Stone sold at the Dungeon Guide Shop.)\n(Not eligible for Enchant Burning.)\n(Not tradable.)",
    3500041: "A Chain Blade modified for advanced players. The complexly shaped blade has increased attack damage.\n(Works with the Upgrade Stone sold at the Dungeon Guide Shop.)\n(Not eligible for Enchant Burning.)\n(Not tradable.)",
    3500042: "Brave Beast Wings",
    3500043: "Lonely Strong Beast Wings",
    3500044: "Desolate Strong Beast Wings",
    3500045: "Brave Strong Beast Wings",
    3500046: "A control bar imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    3500047: "A lute imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    3500048: "A lance imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    3500049: "A pair of knuckles imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    3500050: "Black Rose Bow",
    3500051: "Black Rose Clutch",
    3500052: "An elegant bow inspired by black roses, which are reflected in its beautiful design.",
    3500053: "An elegant evening bag inspired by black roses. Holding it makes you feel like you've just stepped out of a magazine.",
    3500054: "Cotton Boll Branch",
    3500055: "Antique Wooden Dual Gun",
    3500056: "Old Diary",
    3500057: "A branch of cotton bolls that glow with a subtle light. It fits perfectly in your hand.",
    3500058: "A Dual Gun with an elegant design. It is decorated with unique metal embellishments and polished wood grips.",
    3500059: "An old diary that's become well-worn with use and age. The passage of time has rendered it illegible, but it can now be used as a spell book.",
    3500060: "Paper Sword",
