    3500335: "A Wand crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500336: "A wand containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500337: "A Cylinder crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.\nDramatically increases the Alchemic effects of all elements.",
    3500338: "A Control Bar crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500339: "A Two-handed Sword crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500340: "A Knuckle crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500341: "Dual Guns crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from them, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve. It inflicts a powerful shock and knocks back enemies with 3 attacks.",
    3500342: "A shuriken containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500343: "A Chain Blade crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500344: "Special arrows that, when touched, fill one with a chilling emptiness. Use them with the Nightbringer Predator Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\n\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Nightbringer Predator.",
    3500345: "Arrows containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. Use them with the Perseus Voiceless Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\n\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Perseus Voiceless Bow.",
