    3500478: "Celtic Tetra Cylinder (Rental)",
    3500480: "A bow fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Great strength is needed to draw it, but each arrow loosed is driven by that same potent force.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    3500481: "A crossbow fashioned with a dignity befitting a goddess. Elegant and powerful limbs flex to loose bolts that pierce even strong defenses, calling to mind the wrath of the divine.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    3500482: "A wand said to have sprung from the wisdom of a goddess, blending fire, ice, and lightning magics within its core. Designed to empower bolt magic, it grants its wielder greater effectiveness in the casting of Firebolts, Icebolts, and Lightning Bolts when fully upgraded and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    3500483: "A cylinder fashioned in the likeness of a similar implement possessed by a goddess. It greatly enhances the effects of elemental Alchemy skills.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    3500484: "A pair of steel Control Bars fashioned in the likeness of those possessed by a goddess. The precision control they afford allows their wielder to render enemies helpless.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    3500497: "Noble Golf Club Two-handed Axe",
    3500498: "A lance issued to one of the warriors of the frigid north, enhanced by its user. With steel as cold as winter itself, the sight of it makes enemies tremble.",
    3500499: "A lance issued to one of the warriors of the frigid north. With steel as cold as winter itself, the sight of it makes enemies tremble.",
    3500500: "A shield issued to one of the warriors of the frigid north, enhanced by its user. It is made to stand strong against any attack.",
