    3500506: "Lightning Lance",
    3500507: "Lightning Shield",
    3500508: "A lance infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning.",
    3500509: "A shield infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning.",
    3500510: "Lightning Lantern",
    3500511: "A lantern-like apparatus designed to contain a perpetually crackling ball of lightning. Even from within the sealed glass tube, the electric charge makes the hairs on your arm stand on end.",
    3500512: "Wanderer's Pipe Wand",
    3500513: "우아한 플로렌스 무도회 날개",
    3500514: "순수한 플로렌스 무도회 날개",
    3500515: "고결한 플로렌스 무도회 날개",
    3500516: "A legendary blade keen enough to break any bonds, even those of life and death. Spectral blacksmiths labored over its creation for many months.",
    3500517: "A legendary blade keen enough to break any bonds, even those of life and death. Spectral blacksmiths labored over its creation for many months.",
