    3500598: "A chain blade containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500599: "A Chain Blade fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Honed blades embedded in a durable chain render it capable of shredding enemies with whiplike reach and flexibility.",
    3500600: "A Shield crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500601: "A shield containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
