    3500603: "Perseus Arcane Wand (Event)",
    3500604: "Nightbringer Spearhead Lance",
    3500605: "A greataxe containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500606: "A two-handed axe fashioned from a restored great axe said to have been wielded by a goddess. Its broad, sharp double blades strike with unyielding force, inflicting great damage on foes. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.",
    3500607: "Perseus Tormented Knuckles",
    3500608: "Nightbringer Vanquisher Dual Guns",
    3500609: "A special arrow that, when touched, fills one with a chilling emptiness. Use them with the Nightbringer Predator Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Nightbringer Predator.",
    3500610: "An arrow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. Use them with the Perseus Voiceless Bow to loose deadly shots of magical energy.\nCannot be equipped with bows other than the Perseus Voiceless Bow.",
    3500611: "A staff that reflects the generosity of a goddess, enabling the wielder to cast powerful magic attacks or support allies with the Party Healing skill. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    3500612: "Nightbringer Wraith Chain Blade",
    3500613: "A Spell Book crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
