    3500615: "A guard cylinder containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud. Advances in cylinder manufacture allow alchemy crystals to be stored in the outer casing of this guard cylinder, enabling alchemical effects to be produced with stunning alacrity.",
    3500616: "An orb crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    3500617: "An orb containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud, but gazing into reveals only enigmas.",
    3500618: "Lumina Star Wireless Microphone",
    3500619: "A compact microphone custom made for the beloved Lumina Star idol group, tuned to capture and amplify even the most delicate vocals. You must be equipped with a Microphone to sing at low Song skill ranks. However, you will be able to sing without a Microphone once you become a better singer.",
    3500620: "Giant Pinwheel Greatsword",
