    3500646: "A scythe said to be imbued with the cold indifference of a goddess. It is said to possess immense potential, but how much of it can be brought to bear depends on the skill of the wielder.",
    3500647: "Fallen Celestial Daydream Floating Silk",
    3500648: "A sword containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500649: "A hammer containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    3500650: "A one-handed blunt weapon fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Capable of impressive destructive power, it distinguishes itself from other hammers by its stable damage output.",
    3500651: "A one-handed blunt weapon fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Light yet sturdy, it affords its wielder a faster rate of attack than one would expect for a hammer.",
    3500656: "A crossbow fashioned with a dignity befitting a goddess. Elegant and powerful limbs flex to loose bolts that pierce even strong defenses, calling to mind the wrath of the divine.",
