    3500662: "Wonderland Card Suites Shuriken",
    3500663: "A shuriken that is, in reality, a hand of large playing cards held like a fan. Does one throw a single card at a time, or all of them? Perhaps in a topsy-turvy world, such questions need have no answer.",
