    3620000: "A crossbow created from the powerful horn of a unicorn. It shines with steadfast purity, ornamented with roses.",
    5000000: "A Shield crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5000002: "스페셜 켈타리온 포스 웨어(남성용)",
    5000003: "스페셜 켈타리온 포스 웨어(여성용)",
    5000004: "프루츠 블러썸 원드",
    5000005: "A wand containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nThere's a message engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids your journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5000006: "A greathammer fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.",
    5000007: "A greataxe fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Its broad, curved edge can cleave through the toughest targets. Despite its hulking size, both humans and Elves can wield it.",
    5000008: "A staff born of the will of a goddess. Those who upgrade it will find themselves able to more effectively regulate their mana. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    5000009: "A staff that reflects the generosity of a goddess, enabling the wielder to cast powerful magic attacks or support allies with the Party Healing skill. It has the power to call on all magic skills of the three elements and, when held, allows you to use the Meditation skill while running.",
    5000010: "A lance fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. It has been imbued with an ancient power that resounds in the clangor of its blows.",
    5000011: "A pair of knuckles fashioned in the likeness of a pair possessed by a goddess. With thick, rigid metal plating on the outer hand and tipped with a sharp spike, they're capable of turning powerful punches into lethal blows.",
    5000012: "A pair of next-generation guns fashioned in the likeness of firearms possessed by a goddess. Based on the original Dowra SE, this model has been designed with a higher rate of fire, greater ammunition capacity, and more destructive power.",
    5000013: "A shuriken fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Spinning as it flashes through the air, its five sharpened points can slice enemies to ribbons.",
    5000014: "Magic Power Potion (30 min.)",
    5000015: "Celtic Dowra Ace (Event)",
    5000016: "A pair of steel Control Bars fashioned in the likeness of those possessed by a goddess. The precision control they afford allows their wielder to render enemies helpless.",
    5000017: "아름다운 파도를 수호하는 고결한 수호자의 의상. 하늘하늘한 옷자락이 파도를 연상시킨다.",
    5000018: "아름다운 파도를 수호하는 고귀한 수호자의 의상. 하늘하늘한 옷자락이 파도를 연상시킨다. 입으면 특별한 모션을 취할 수 있다.",
    5000019: "아름다운 파도를 수호하는 고귀한 수호자의 의상. 하늘하늘한 옷자락이 파도를 연상시킨다.",
