    5000024: "An outfit designed by BLEUGENNE by Bleugenne Cosmetics, a subsidiary of the famous Bleugenne Viola brand. While this brand was originally known for its lines of makeup and cologne, it's quickly making waves in the fashion world.",
    5000025: "Brilliant Lumina Star Ribbon Wings",
    5000026: "A dashing cape that complements the elegance of a fancy dress uniform. Drape it over your shoulders to instantly be recognized among fans as the most regal member of your idol group.\n\n(Enchantable, Dyeable)",
