    5000066: "A short ponytail wig done up in a style popular among the Raving Rabbit crew. It has an appealingly roguish look to it, like the hair was casually tied back on the way out the door.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
