    5000081: "Potent High Speed Gathering Potion",
    5000082: "An advanced flying support puppet modeled after Cerise, complete with the same bright, upbeat energy that'll bring a little light to even the darkest dungeon. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which orb will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5000083: "Light Magic Power Potion (30 min.)",
