    5000111: "Fir Bolg Soldier's Gloves (Not to be Distributed)",
    5000115: "An original take on a classic design, cut and sewn in Ailionoa's boutique in Emain Macha. When you need to dress to impress, you can always count on time-tested styles to help you stand out from the crowd. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
