    5000123: "Magic Power Potion (30 min.) (Not tradable)",
    5000124: "A wig styled to complement the fashions produced at Tre'imhse Cairde, but perfectly wearable with a wide variety of clothes.",
    5000126: "Sweet Barista Uniform (M)",
    5000127: "Sweet Barista Uniform (F)",
    5000128: "A uniform worn by baristas who know their light roasts from their dark roasts. The rich aroma of coffee seems to waft from the apron, enticing many to consider ordering just one more cup.",
    5000129: "A uniform worn by baristas who know their light roasts from their dark roasts. The rich aroma of coffee seems to waft from the apron, enticing many to consider ordering just one more cup.",
    5000130: "Ailionoa Chic Gloves (M)",
