    5000133: "Ailionoa Chic Shoes (F)",
    5000134: "켈타리온 포스 손 장식(여성용)",
    5000135: "'Before her eyes, the God of Death's jet-black hair turned white as snow.' -- Excerpt from the fairy tale 'Frozen Heart'\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000136: "An outfit designed to highlight the noble spirit of the Royal Brawlers. These clothes mark the wearer as a martial artist of high caliber, recognized by the kingdom. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000137: "어둠을 가르는 까마귀의 치명적인 기운이 서린 헬름. 날카롭고 우아한 외형이 눈길을 사로잡는다.\n(톨리와 친구들의 화이트데이 이벤트 기간 동안 착용 가능하며, 매주 목요일 오전 7시마다 삭제됩니다.)",
    5000140: "A uniform favored by crews on ships sailing the temperate southern seas. You may not know when you'll next make port, but at least you'll look great when you get there. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5000141: "An outfit perfect for spending a hot summer day at the beach. The prominent henna on the left arm lends a touch of island style with its tropical leaf design.",
    5000142: "An outfit perfect for spending a hot summer day at the beach. The bikini's tropical leaf pattern lends a touch of island style that's sure to turn heads.",
    5000143: "Special Celestial Eminence Autumn Cyclas (M)",
    5000144: "Sestia Academy Hat (M) (Tolly's Fashion)",
    5000150: "Gloves with a mysterious quality, like the essence of the waning moon. The elegant detailing on the wrist and hand captures the eye.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000151: "마법의 기운이 담긴 문양들로 장식된 부츠. 강렬한 몽환의 기운이 느껴진다.\n(톨리와 친구들의 러브 프로듀스 기간 동안 착용 가능하며, 매주 목요일 오전 7시마다 삭제됩니다.)",
    5000152: "마법의 기운이 담긴 문양과 리본으로 장식된 힐. 나릇한 몽환의 매력이 느껴진다.\n(톨리와 친구들의 러브 프로듀스 기간 동안 착용 가능하며, 매주 목요일 오전 7시마다 삭제됩니다.)",
    5000153: "Shoes that emphasize a small draconian's cuteness. The pattern on the top of the foot and around the ankle area add elegant accents.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000154: "Shoes that make good use of a small draconian's cuteness. The frills on the top of the foot, and the small ribbon at the back, are eye-catching.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000155: "A pair of stylish loafers designed by Ailionoa. They exude an understated elegance.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000156: "A pair of stylish heels designed by Ailionoa. They exude an understated elegance.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000157: "These combat boots are designed to protect your feet in any environment, and provide extra grip for climbing walls. They've even got an extra hidden pocket in the heel. They're an important tool for top-secret missions.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000158: "These combat boots are designed to protect your feet in any environment, and provide extra grip for climbing walls. They've even got an extra hidden pocket in the heel. They're an important tool for top-secret missions.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5000159: "Moonlit Howls Shoes (M) (Tolly's Fashion)",
