    5000163: "A slicked-back hairstyle to stay out of your face for long days on the range. The rough and tumble look is perfect for an independent soul.",
    5000164: "Long wavy hair that falls past the waist, perfect for catching the wind on horseback. The rough and tumble look is perfect for an independent soul.",
    5000165: "An outfit featuring a long leather duster with an embossed bull emblem on the back. With plenty of hidden pockets, pouches, and holsters, you'll always be ready for a quick draw. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5000166: "An outfit featuring a long leather duster with an embossed bull emblem on the back. With plenty of hidden pockets, pouches, and holsters, you'll always be ready for a quick draw.",
