    5000196: "A simple wristband that's stylish and functional. The embroidered logo looks familiar.",
    5000197: "This fashionable headband gives you your very own pair of adorable cat ears that wiggle on their own, and plenty of lace ruffles besides. Though not standard-issue for maids and butlers, they lend the wearer a spry playfulness favored by surprisingly many nobles.",
