    5010005: "A delicate pair of wings wrought by fairies who dwell deep in a mysterious glade. Take wing upon the breeze and hear the song of the winds.",
    5010006: "A delicate pair of wings wrought by fairies who dwell deep in a mysterious glade. Take wing upon the breeze and hear the song of the winds.",
    5010007: "A delicate pair of wings wrought by fairies who dwell deep in a mysterious glade. Take wing upon the breeze and hear the song of the winds.",
    5010008: "A gossamer pair of wings wrought by fairies who dwell deep in a sun-dappled glade. Take wing upon the breeze and hear the song of the winds.",
    5010010: "A warm fur coat, perfect for keeping warm in winter or just for looking classy. It hangs gracefully off your shoulders, and never falls off.",
    5010011: "A warm fur coat, perfect for keeping warm in winter or just for looking classy. It hangs gracefully off your shoulders, and never falls off.",
    5010012: "A warm fur coat, perfect for keeping warm in winter or just for looking classy. It hangs gracefully off your shoulders, and never falls off.",
