    5010015: "A pair of compact yet powerful wings with a unique shape. Perfect for when you need to spread your wings in a crowded area.",
    5010016: "A pair of compact yet powerful wings with a unique shape. Perfect for when you need to spread your wings in a crowded area.",
    5010017: "A pair of compact yet powerful wings with a unique shape. Perfect for when you need to spread your wings in a crowded area.",
    5010018: "Wings flush with smooth, beautiful feathers. They possess a delicate, heavenly grace.",
    5010019: "A pair of soft, downy wings that lets you fly amongst the sweetest dreams.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010020: "Wings with a mysterious quality, like the essence of the waning moon. The gorgeous draping captures the eye.\n(Dyeable; the B part has transparency and will become more transparent the closer it is to 0.)",
    5010021: "Wings imbued with a darkly alluring magic. Many are drawn to the sense of mystery they exude.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010022: "Fashioned after Brilluen's wings. Wearing this will make you feel as powerful as Brilluen, so much so that you'll actually be able to fly!\n(Dyeable)",
    5010023: "A pair of wings imbued with a primordial energy that existed before even the elements. Wearing them, you can almost feel the pulse of the world in its infancy.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010024: "A pair of wings that seems almost like a mirage made manifest. The breeze moves through them in an unfamiliar way. Will they be powerful enough to reach the land beyond the scorching sun?\n(Dyeable)",
    5010025: "Shining wings imbued with the essence of the night sky. Each movement, great or small, seems to shake loose motes of twinkling stardust.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010026: "Radiant wings that invoke the sun with their fiery beauty. Their bold brilliance inspires awe in all who gaze upon them.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010027: "Mystical wings that pay homage to the moon with their elegance. The enigmatic detail of their intricate design makes them all the more alluring.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010028: "A pair of wings covered with sleek, beautiful feathers. The way they flutter while running makes the wearer look heaven-sent.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010029: "A pair of graceful wings that looks ready to catch the wind with their unique shape. They flap beautifully as you run.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010030: "A large pair of wings that is sure to stand out in glorious colors. They flap elegantly as you run.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010031: "A pair of wings with a wide and noble wingspan. They look ready to soar in the wide-open sky.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010032: "A pair of compact yet powerful wings with a unique shape. Perfect for when you need to spread your wings in a crowded area.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010033: "A pair of wings covered with sleek, beautiful feathers. The way they flutter while running makes the wearer look heaven-sent.",
    5010034: "A warm fur coat, perfect for keeping warm in winter or just for looking classy. It hangs gracefully off your shoulders, and never falls off.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010035: "A pair of wings that are extend downwards towards the waist before arcing upwards. The graceful shape is reminiscent of dancers at a ball.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010036: "A pair of graceful wings that looks ready to catch the wind with their unique shape. They flap beautifully as you run.",
    5010037: "A pair of compact yet powerful wings with a unique shape. Perfect for when you need to spread your wings in a crowded area.",
    5010038: "A large pair of wings that is sure to stand out in glorious colors. They flap elegantly as you run.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010039: "A pair of wings made from the softest feathers, to make you feel angelic. Each and every wingbeat is full of wonder.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010040: "Wings flush with stiff, compact feathers. Their bladelike rigidity lends itself to slight, restrained movements.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010041: "Wings designed by Bleugenne Viola with a design inspired by images of angelic beings. Being good doesn't mean you can't be sinfully fashionable.\n(Dyeable)",
    5010042: "Wings flush with long, rough feathers. The traces of a fierce battle can be seen in their scarring.\n(Dyeable)",
