    5010047: "A sleek and stylish outfit of a crop top, skort, and jean jacket. It's so comfortable you'll want to wear it every day of the week. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5010048: "A simple and stylish outfit of a hoodie, shorts, and crossbody bag. It's so comfortable you'll want to wear it every day of the week.",
    5010049: "A sleek and stylish outfit of a crop top, skort, and jean jacket. It's so comfortable you'll want to wear it every day of the week.",
    5010050: "A sporty and supportive wristband to help you with your day-to-day tasks. The simple look is complemented by an eye-catching hand tattoo.",
    5010051: "You never know when you'll need an extra scrunchie! For extra personality, this one comes with a bracelet for your other hand and some cute rings.",
    5010052: "A sleek, simple pair of athletic shoes. With durable materials, a comfortable sole, and good ankle support, they'll take you anywhere you want to go.",
