    5010066: "Elegant, well-crafted, and only for the crazy rich. Perfect for any social occasion where you need to dress to impress.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
