    5020001: "A lyre inspired by the sight of the sun rising over the sea. The oceanic motif shines through in the mermaid's tail and elegant clamshell styling. If you stand on the shore at daybreak and play, your music will resound over the crashing of the waves.",
    5020002: "A shield carried into battle by the guardians who safeguard the seas. The wave symbol upon its surface serves as a proud representation of what its bearer fights to protect.",
    5020003: "Dawntide Fishing Rod",
    5020004: "The iconic compact by Bleugenne Cosmetics. With Bleugenne in your pocket, you can stay flawless in any situation.",
