    5020008: "Piat Sestia Academy Puppy Plushie",
    5020009: "This adorable kitty plushie is the perfect size to hug with both arms, and fills you with feelings of safety and warmth. It's a perfect companion for students on a journey for knowledge, as well as anyone else who could use a hug.",
