    5020028: "Noble Imperial Knight Ceremonial Cape",
    5020029: "Dazzling Imperial Knight Ceremonial Cape",
    5020030: "A cylinder fashioned in the likeness of a similar implement possessed by a goddess. It greatly enhances the effects of elemental Alchemy skills.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    5020031: "A pair of gloves worn by the guardians who safeguard the seas. Much like water, hands are capable of being both gentle and forceful.",
