    5020034: "Ethereal Devil Scythe",
    5020035: "A pair of knuckles fashioned in the likeness of a pair possessed by a goddess. With thick, rigid metal plating on the outer hand and tipped with a sharp spike, they're capable of turning powerful punches into lethal blows.",
    5020037: "Celtic Clashing Lance",
    5020038: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
