    5020048: "Fallen Eternia Featherlight Wings",
    5020049: "A shuriken that is, in reality, a hand of large playing cards held like a fan. Does one throw a single card at a time, or all of them? Perhaps in a topsy-turvy world, such questions need have no answer.",
    5020050: "Harmonious Magic Powder (Event)",
    5020051: "A mischievous raccoon tail, thick and squeezable with the recognizable banded pattern along its length. It's perfect for adding a splash of personality to your look.",
    5020052: "A cunning leopard tail that ensures you'll be the first to be spotted in any crowd. It's perfect for adding a splash of personality to your look.",
