    5020098: "A large captain's hat perched atop long, beautiful hair. An eye patch covers one eye. The fur atop the hat gives the look a bit of extra flair.\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5020099: "A wig with a beautiful moon ornament atop a long, natural hairstyle. This look exudes sophistication!\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5020100: "A wig with a beautiful butterfly ornament atop loosely braided long hair. This look exudes sophistication!\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5020101: "A refined wig that instantly puts your hairstyling on the level of the guests at a high-class getaway. So luxuriant, only your stylist will know it's not your real hair.\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
