    5030413: "Handwear designed to go the distance during outdoor activities. It has a wristband on one hand and a half-glove on the other.\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5030414: "A pair of ornate pirate gloves. The well-trimmed leather gives it a sturdy look.\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5030415: "An accessory for your wrist that makes you look like a fairy. It adds the perfect touch of beauty and elegance.\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5030416: "Come one! Come all! And witness the amazing feats of fashion and daring dressing-room deeds that you will accomplish in these stunning circus performer's gloves! Create quick-fingered miracles and high-diving stunts with equal panache!\n\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5030417: "Special Punk Rocker Outfit (M)",
    5030418: "Special Punk Rocker Outfit (F)",
    5030419: "Punk Rocker Outfit (M)",
    5030420: "Punk Rocker Outfit (F)",
    5030421: "Only those who defeated Languhiris the White Dragon are worthy to don these boots. Made through Blacksmithing rather than Magic Craft, this protective footwear offers greater power, though at the cost of the original's magic resistance.\n\nA message is engraved on one.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5030422: "Only those who defeated Languhiris the White Dragon are worthy to don these boots. Made through Blacksmithing rather than Magic Craft, this protective footwear offers greater power, though at the cost of the original's magic resistance.\n\nA message is engraved on one.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
