    5040234: "A replica of the rings worn by Hymerark. The quality of the metalwork is godly.",
    5040235: "Day Tripper Watch and Strap (M)",
    5040239: "Come one! Come all! And witness the amazing feats of fashion and daring dressing-room deeds that you will accomplish in this showy circus performer's outfit! Show off your superhuman skills and catch the eye of the most jaded audience in seconds! Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose!",
    5040240: "Come one! Come all! And witness the amazing feats of fashion and daring dressing-room deeds that you will accomplish in this showy circus performer's outfit! Show off your superhuman skills and catch the eye of the most jaded audience in seconds! Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose!",
    5040245: "An outfit worn by bakers and servers at the Blanc Patisserie, purveyors of decadent cakes, pastries, and other mouth-watering desserts. With every stitch and button thoughtfully considered, these fancy clothes are every bit as charming as the shop's sweets.",
    5040246: "가벼운 외출에 어울리도록 제작된 웨이프런 원피스. 짧은 여행용 트렁크를 든 다소곳한 몸짓에서 기분 좋은 설렘이 느껴진다. 입으면 특별한 모션을 취할 수 있다.",
    5040247: "Special Charming Romantic Lace Dress (F)",
    5040248: "Romantic Lace Heels (F)",
    5040249: "A pair of gloves as soft and delicate as a touch from your special someone's hand. The luxurious lace details elevate any look.",
