    5040303: "A smart and studious wig, perfect for a busy student in the big city. Look your best and ace your tests!",
    5040306: "A smart and studious uniform, perfect for a busy student in the big city. You may pass by crowds of others wearing the same on your walk to school in the morning, but you wear it best. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5040307: "A pair of gloves designed to resemble those worn by Rowan. The dark color is perfect to avoid staining.",
    5040308: "A pair of gloves designed to resemble those worn by Rowan. The dark color is perfect to avoid staining.",
    5040309: "사랑스러운 디자인의 여성용 가발. 금방이라도 달콤한 사랑에 빠질 것처럼 매력적이다.",
    5040310: "사랑스러운 디자인의 여성용 가발과 머리장식. 금방이라도 달콤한 사랑에 빠질 것처럼 매력적이다.",
