    5040370: "A pair of custom-made, high-quality boots for high-ranking knights.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
