    5050002: "A Spell Book crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5050004: "Born from ancient Celtic legends, this mighty weapon embodies both nature's generosity and wrath. The moment it touches your hand, a powerful vibration surges through it--as if responding to your very will.",
    5050005: "Exquisite Reforging Tool",
    5050006: "Precise Reforging Tool",
    5050007: "Surging Hope Gem",
    5050008: "Blossoming Hope Gem",
