    5120022: "A heart-shaped glow wand that glows brilliantly at night. Be warned that this item only lasts for 2 hours after purchase. It will vanish automatically upon expiring.",
    5120023: "High-tech combat-equipped wings used by a resistance fighter who never gives in to tyranny. The Gatling guns on each side won't run out of bullets until the forces of justice are triumphant.",
    5120024: "A ball used for playing basketball. Show off your baller skills with it. Swish!",
    5120025: "Hard Mode Ciar Advanced Fomor Pass (Event)",
    5120026: "Hard Mode Alby Advanced Fomor Pass (Event)",
    5120027: "Hard Mode Rundal Advanced Fomor Pass (Event)",
    5120028: "A pair of control bars containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. Once a puppeteer grows accustomed to the discomfort of manipulating these bars, they will be rewarded with a marked improvement in the performance of their marionette, which will show itself to be as ruthless as it is flamboyant.\n\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, speak with the NPC you rented it from.",
    5120029: "Arrows imbued with pure lightning-elemental energy. Surges of electricity crackle up and down their shafts.",
