    5120048: "Hyperion Eclipse Helionic Helm",
    5120049: "Hyperion Eclipse Selenian Diadema",
    5120050: "Celestial headwear that shines with the radiance of the sun. The wings on each side confer upon the wearer an authoritative presence.",
    5120051: "Celestial headwear that gleams with the luster of the moon. The detailing on its veil confers upon the wearer an alluring mystique.",
