    5120063: "Hyperion Eclipse Full Chiton (F)",
    5120064: "A finely made tunic replete with the radiant energy of the sun. Ornamented with detailed metalwork stylized to represent solar light, it has been enchanted with a mysterious spell that allows the wearer to take on another form. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5120065: "A finely made tunic replete with the tranquil energy of the moon. Ornamented with detailed metalwork stylized to represent lunar light, it has been enchanted with a mysterious spell that allows the wearer to take on another form. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5120066: "A finely made tunic replete with the radiant energy of the sun. It is ornamented with detailed metalwork stylized to represent solar light.",
    5120067: "A finely made tunic replete with the tranquil energy of the moon. It is ornamented with detailed metalwork stylized to represent lunar light.",
    5120068: "A finely made tunic replete with the radiant energy of the sun. Ornamented with detailed metalwork and flamelike embroidery stylized to represent solar light, it has been enchanted with a mysterious spell that allows the wearer to take on another form. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5120069: "A finely made tunic replete with the tranquil energy of the moon. Ornamented with detailed metalwork and a full-length skirt stylized to represent lunar light, it has been enchanted with a mysterious spell that allows the wearer to take on another form. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5120070: "A finely made tunic replete with the radiant energy of the sun. It is ornamented with detailed metalwork and flamelike embroidery stylized to represent solar light.",
    5120071: "A finely made tunic replete with the tranquil energy of the moon. It is ornamented with detailed metalwork and a full-length skirt stylized to represent lunar light.",
