    5140002: "Dragon's Broken Sword",
    5140003: "An orb that holds the echoes of an ancient dragon's power. The sense of majesty and nobility you feel when touching it could bring anyone to tears.",
    5140004: "Although this sword is broken, an uncanny energy completes the blade with a deadly sting. Legend has it that the dragon that broke this sword bled a single drop of blood onto it, infusing it with the dragon's own power.",
    5140005: "Ewan's Shoe (Right) (Not to be Distributed)",
    5140006: "Ewan's Shoe (Left) (Not to be Distributed)",
    5140007: "Long ago, when Ewan was a young boy and Nari a young girl, Ewan gave Nari this shoe.",
    5140008: "Long ago, when Ewan was a young boy and Nari a young girl, Ewan gave Nari this shoe.",
    5140009: "Moonshadow Emissary's Scythe",
    5140010: "Duskveil Emissary's Scythe",
    5140011: "A great scythe sometimes carried by the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next. While the Moonshadow Emissaries are not held to be reapers of souls, few would dispute their effectiveness in such a role, especially when wielding such an imposing weapon.",
    5140012: "A lance fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. It has been imbued with an ancient power that resounds in the clangor of its blows.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    5160000: "A set of earrings that are clearly visible even when moving around on stage. You can equip them along with some hat items.",
    5160001: "Forgotten Nightmare Sword",
    5160002: "A spellbook containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    5160003: "A gossamer pair of wings wrought by fairies who dwell deep in a sun-dappled glade. Take wing upon the breeze and hear the song of the winds.",
    5160004: "Lovely Folded Secret Forest Wings",
    5160005: "A staff wrought from ancient and hallowed wood. Replete with nature's blessings, it is a favored weapon of those who wander the forests, sworn to protect the wildlands.",
    5160006: "A scythe crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5160007: "A scythe containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    5160012: "Glorious Miniopterus Wings",
    5160013: "A pair of wings with a wide and noble wingspan. They look ready to soar in the wide-open sky.",
    5160014: "A pair of graceful wings that looks ready to catch the wind with their unique shape. They flap beautifully as you run.",
    5160015: "An earring infused with the crackling energy of a thunderbolt. Its stately design cradles an undulating ball of condensed lightning. You can equip it along with some hat items.",
    5160016: "Long wavy hair that falls past the waist, perfect for catching the wind on horseback. The rough and tumble look is perfect for an independent soul.",
    5160017: "Refashioned Coco Sailor Mini",
    5160018: "Refashioned Mini Leather Dress",
    5160019: "A stylish and comfy jumpsuit with a festive look. Just put it on and you're ready to party. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5160020: "A uniform that's as sweet and lovely as a bouquet of fresh flowers. It's decorated with real flowers to show off your skill in the florist's trade. As a side effect, it'll keep you smelling fresh as a daisy no matter how long your day is.",
