    5250255: "Special Falcon of Sunrise Outfit (F)",
    5250256: "Glenn Bearna Additional Entry Pass",
    5250264: "Luxurious light armor with an imposing charm. A specially crafted plate covers the chest, providing excellent protection to vital areas while still allowing for swift and dexterous movement.\n\nA message is engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
