    5250290: "Tech Duinn Mission Additional Entry Pass (Tradable)",
    5250291: "Celestial headwear that gleams with the luster of the moon. The detailing on its veil confers upon the wearer an alluring mystique.",
    5250293: "A wig with a style that somehow exudes a feeling of a sadness and longing from a time before the arrival of mankind. You can sense both corruption and blessing in each strand, but fortunately, it is also highly fashionable.",
    5250294: "어둠을 가르는 까마귀의 치명적인 기운이 서린 아머. 섬세한 장식과 우아한 외형이 눈길을 사로잡는다. 입으면 특별한 모션을 취할 수 있다.",
