    5300005: "A majestic crescent blade that's seen countless battlefields. Weighing in at 82 kati, even a single swing carries devastation beyond death.",
    5300006: "A majestic crescent blade that's seen countless battlefields. Weighing in at 82 kati, even a single swing carries devastation beyond death.",
    5300008: "Lucent Neon Mandolin",
    5300009: "Raving Rabbit Shuriken",
    5300017: "A bow fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Great strength is needed to draw it, but each arrow loosed is driven by that same potent force.\n<color=1>This weapon has been restored in Avon. (Not tradable)</color>",
    5300018: "A Two-handed Axe crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5300021: "Circus Bandmember's Drums",
    5300022: "Charming Romantic Lace Fan",
    5300025: "A Pihne pixel balloon! Equip it to revive instantly when incapacitated. Can be used up to 5 times.",
    5300026: "A Talvish pixel balloon! Equip it to revive instantly when incapacitated. Can be used up to 5 times.",
