    5300036: "Royal Society Sponsorship Badge",
    5300039: "Moonlit Puffy Cat Tail (1 Year)",
    5300051: "Ferghus-made Fallen Pierrot Marionette",
    5300052: "A pierrot marionette that has withstood Ferghus's zealous hammering. If anything seems off, it's probably just your imagination.\n\nA small engraving, legible only upon close inspection, reads, \"<color=1>It takes a REAL man to love dolls.</color>\"",
    5300053: "고스트펑크의 일원들이 다루는 대형 낫. 다양한 전술을 수행하기 위한 기계 구조 설계가 돋보인다.",
    5300054: "Adamantine Coin",
    5300055: "An advanced support puppet modeled after the popular virtual star Nering, a charming fairy who has captured the hearts of viewers around the world. She's always ready to hit the \"Like\" button for you. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5300057: "블루젠 브랜드의 대표적인 여성용 드레스. 매력적인 디자인과 재질로, 블루젠의 우아한 로고가 장식되어 있다.(거래 불가)",
    5300060: "신선한 사과가 들어가 있어보이는 백팩. 하트 모양의 가방에 담긴 탐스럽게 생긴 사과를 보니 한 입 베어 물고 싶어 진다.",
    5300061: "Fallen Enchanting Piat Wings",
    5300068: "A halo imbued with the grim aura of the ravens who descend in the wake of battles to feast upon the slain. Its many-winged flourishes are punctuated by several eye-catching gemstones.",
    5300076: "Fresh Dewdrop",
    5300077: "A sleek, simple pair of athletic shoes. With durable materials, a comfortable sole, and good ankle support, they'll take you anywhere you want to go.",
    5300078: "A cute bucket hat to keep the sun out of your eyes while you're out gathering flowers. The floral decorations give it a touch of elegance.",
    5300081: "Special Trendy Day Tripper Wear (F)",
    5300086: "OX 퀴즈 증표",
    5300090: "Tiny Starbrite",
    5300093: "A slightly tousled long wig with cute buns. Perfect for when you wake up feeling fresh as a daisy.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5300102: "Hand ornaments in the shape of dragon talons. Well, they're called ornaments, but they certainly look sharp...\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
