    5310001: "A finely fashioned longbow that seems as much an objet d'art as it is a functional weapon. Its delicate, sweeping curves are accented with jewels that shine with a gleaming luster.",
    5310002: "A wand suffused with tranquil lunar energy. The crescent shape has long been believed to be an effective focus for gathering and shaping mana.",
    5310003: "A leopard tail with a spotted pattern. Quite elegant.",
    5310004: "Pure Moonlit Howls Wings",
    5310005: "Fallen Moonlit Howls Wings",
    5310006: "Sylvan Strider Sacred Grove Staff",
    5310007: "A two-handed hammer fashioned from a restored hammer said to have been wielded by a goddess in judgment of her foes. Despite its hulking size and the destructive power of which it is capable, both humans and Elves can wield it with ease.\nAs this item is a rental weapon, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this weapon from your inventory, visit NPC Sasha.",
    5310009: "Perseus Voiceless Arrows",
