    5310035: "The wig of a resistance fighter who never gives in to tyranny. While it's sometimes necessary for a resistance member to disguise their identity, they can never hide their iron will and fighting spirit.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5310036: "The outfit of a resistance fighter who never gives in to tyranny. The bravest of resistance members wear their convictions on their sleeve, no matter the danger. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5310037: "The simple yet refined uniform of Crocus High School. The cardigan will keep you toasty warm in the cooler months. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5310038: "Ethereal Ballet Slippers (F)",
    5310039: "신비한 비밀을 간직한 화원에 등장하는 소녀에게 어울릴 것 같은 가발이다. 부드럽게 떨어지는 웨이브의 우아함 속에 세련미를 함께 느낄 수 있다.",
    5310040: "Crafted with care from fine leather and warm fur, these boots will stand up to long hunts in deep snow. They are prized by those who live hand-in-claw with powerful birds of prey.",
