    5500000: "This two-handed sword was once wielded by a leader in a dark cult. The sharp blade is imbued with a mysterious invisible energy. When sheathed, the darkness appears suppressed.",
    5500001: "A majestic crescent blade that's seen countless battlefields. Weighing in at 82 kati, even a single swing carries devastation beyond death.",
    5500002: "A replica of the Scales of Obedience.",
    5500003: "프릴과 리본으로 장식된 고풍스러운 우산이다. 뜨거운 태양과 시원한 비를 막아줄 수 있을 듯하다.",
    5500004: "쥬얼 모나크 롱 블레이드",
    5500005: "A greatsword containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, speak with the NPC you rented it from.",
    5500006: "Celtic Guardian Staff",
    5500008: "Festive Eastern Fireworks Lance",
    5500009: "The tail of a dragon, scaly and studded with a long spike on the end. If you don't get your foe in the beginning, now they can catch the tail end of your assault.",
    5500010: "This headband will give you the noble, powerful ears and spiral antlers of a desert antelope.",
    5500011: "A stylish ensemble worn by up-and-coming idols making their first live concert debut. Dressed in these clothes, you can feel the tension of the stage and the hopes of winning the hearts of audiences near and far. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5500012: "A stylish ensemble worn by up-and-coming idols making their first live concert debut. Dressed in these clothes, you can feel the tension of the stage and the hopes of winning the hearts of audiences near and far. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5500013: "Elysees Manor Cat Eared Lace Headband",
    5500014: "16th Anniversary Luxury Equipment Bag",
    5500015: "A proper clothing version of the Hebona Robe, said to enhance the fundamental Bolt Magic spells. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater magical power.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    5500016: "A proper clothing version of the Hebona Robe, said to enhance the fundamental Bolt Magic spells. Fashioned from higher-end materials, it boasts improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater magical power.\n\nA message is embroidered on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
