    5510000: "A Lance crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5530007: "A lance fashioned into a harpoon, favored by crews on ships sailing the temperate southern seas for fending off giant creatures from the briny deep.",
    5530009: "Iana is known to blend timeless elegance with modern sass. This thousand-year-old advanced support puppet modeled on her is sure to fly into your stream and mesmerize your audience. This isn't just a collab--it's an unprecedented, unmissable phenomenon! Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5530010: "An advanced support puppet blending both timeless beauty and modern sass, Iana is sure to fly into your stream and mesmerize your audience. This isn't just a collab--it's an unprecedented, unmissable phenomenon! Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5530011: "Smash that \"Like\" button and every challenge that comes your way with this thousand-year-old advanced support puppet, meticulously modeled after Nering. This enchanting fairy has already stolen the hearts of millions and is ready to raid your livestream! Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5530012: "Smash that \"Like\" button and every challenge that comes your way with this advanced support puppet, meticulously modeled after Nering. This enchanting fairy has already stolen the hearts of millions and is ready to raid your livestream! Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
