    5560147: "Demolition Breaker Arrows",
    5560148: "Hellfire Tilaka (Facewear)",
    5560149: "A mark traditionally applied to the forehead. The elegant flame-like design of this bindi signifies one given the authority to preside over the fiery chasms of hell. You can equip it along with some hat items.",
    5560150: "A detailed design traditionally applied to the forehead and face. The intricate flame-like flourishes of this tilaka signify one given the authority to preside over the fiery chasms of hell. You can equip it along with some hat items.",
    5560151: "Glorious Dazzling Debut Celebrity Backdrop",
    5560152: "Elegant Dazzling Debut Celebrity Backdrop",
    5560153: "Fallen Dazzling Debut Celebrity Backdrop",
    5560154: "Pure Dazzling Debut Celebrity Backdrop",
    5560155: "A frame displayed behind you that adds the perfect dash of pizzazz, turning any occasion into a prime photo op. Favored by up-and-coming idols hoping to win the hearts of audiences near and far.\n(Dyeable)",
    5560156: "A frame displayed behind you that adds the perfect dash of pizzazz, turning any occasion into a prime photo op. Favored by up-and-coming idols hoping to win the hearts of audiences near and far.",
