    5560159: "Battle Astrology Eligibility Certificate",
    5560160: "Proof of your eligibility, given when all Battle Astrology skills that can be advanced to Dan 3 have attained that rank.",
    5560161: "Winter Snowbell Violin",
    5560162: "Winter Snowbell Mandolin",
    5560163: "Winter Snowbell Cello",
    5560164: "A violin fashioned in a winter motif, almost looking like it was taken straight from the pages of a fairy tale. A residual chill hangs over it, giving it a resonance that lends a crisp, clear tone to the music played upon it.",
    5560165: "A mandolin fashioned in a winter motif, almost looking like it was taken straight from the pages of a fairy tale. A residual chill hangs over it, giving it a resonance that lends a crisp, clear tone to the music played upon it.",
    5560166: "A cello fashioned in a winter motif, almost looking like it was taken straight from the pages of a fairy tale. A residual chill hangs over it, giving it a resonance that lends a crisp, clear tone to the music played upon it.\n\nRight-click and select 'Use' to take out the cello or put it away.",
    5560167: "신성한 기운으로 응축시킨 헤일로. 경건한 분위기가 느껴진다.",
    5560168: "신성한 기운으로 응축시킨 헤일로. 경건한 분위기가 느껴진다.",
    5560169: "Red Heart Wings",
    5560170: "An adorable pair of heart-shaped wings that shines in red. Soar through the skies in lovey-dovey style!",
    5560171: "Booksprite Support Puppet",
    5560172: "Elder Booksprite Spirit Support Puppet",
    5560173: "A support puppet that takes the shape of a booksprite from the Library of Secrets. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, or cast a magic shield to protect you.\n\nRight-click while it is equipped to <color=1>activate.</color>. It can be activated for <color=1>2 hours each day</color>.\nActivation time <color=1>resets daily at 7:00 AM (Server Time)</color>.",
    5560174: "A support puppet that takes the shape of an elder booksprite from the Library of Secrets. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, or cast a magic shield to protect you.\n\nRight-click while it is equipped to <color=1>activate.</color>. It can be activated for <color=1>2 hours each day</color>.\nActivation time <color=1>resets daily at 7:00 AM (Server Time)</color>.",
    5560175: "Nightbringer Rogue Crossbow",
    5560176: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow",
    5560177: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow",
    5560178: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow (Rental)",
    5560179: "Nightbringer Rogue Crossbow",
    5560180: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow",
    5560181: "Nightbringer Rogue Crossbow (Event)",
    5560182: "Perseus Dynamic Crossbow (Event)",
    5560183: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5560184: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    5560185: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nThere's a message engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids your journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5560186: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    5560187: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5560188: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    5560189: "A crossbow crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5560190: "A crossbow containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.",
    5560191: "하늘하늘한 지느러미로 만들어진 꼬리. 착용하면 뒷모습에서 지느러미가 신비롭게 흔들리는 모습을 볼 수 있다.",
    5560192: "하늘하늘한 지느러미로 만들어진 꼬리. 착용하면 뒷모습에서 지느러미가 신비롭게 흔들리는 모습을 볼 수 있다.",
    5560193: "아이돌이 무대 위를 비상할 때 착용하는 꼬리. 새가 비상하는 외형이 눈길을 사로잡는다.",
    5560194: "화려한 깃털 외형을 형상화한 꼬리. 섬세한 장식과 아름다운 깃털이 눈길을 사로잡는다.",
    5560195: "Nightbringer Moderator Guard Cylinder",
    5560196: "A guard cylinder crafted from crystallized Erg and adamantine. A faint but unmistakably ominous aura emanates from it, settling over you like the chill of a winter's eve.",
    5560197: "여러 도구와 벨트가 달린 장식 꼬리. 언제 어디서든 작업이 가능해 보인다.",
    5560198: "아름다운 꽃과 리본으로 치장된 꼬리. 간소하지만 우아한 매력이 느껴진다.",
    5560199: "여러 도구와 벨트가 달린 장식 꼬리. 언제 어디서든 작업이 가능해 보인다.",
    5560200: "아름다운 꽃과 리본으로 치장된 꼬리. 간소하지만 우아한 매력이 느껴진다.",
    5560201: "Primitive Stone Axe (Axe)",
