    5560398: "The simple yet refined uniform of Crocus High School. The cardigan will keep you toasty warm in the cooler months.",
    5560399: "The simple yet refined uniform of Crocus High School. The matching tie and pleated pants make this a classic look.",
    5560400: "A helm made to complement suits of Refined Dustin Silver Knight Armor. Its unique construction, featuring overlapping scutes, adds the necessary resilience to shield one's head from all manner of blows. The decorations trailing from the back lend the wearer a sense of poise and dignity.",
    5560401: "A helm made to complement suits of Refined Dustin Silver Knight Armor. Its unique construction, featuring overlapping scutes, adds the necessary resilience to shield one's head from all manner of blows. The decorations trailing from the back lend the wearer a sense of poise and dignity.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    5560402: "A helm made to complement suits of Refined Dustin Silver Knight Armor. Its unique construction, featuring overlapping scutes, adds the necessary resilience to shield one's head from all manner of blows. The decorations trailing from the back lend the wearer a sense of poise and dignity.\n\nA message is engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5560403: "Luxurious heavy armor tailored for veteran knights. The thick fabric pads the wearer's body against sharp, striking blows. Crafted using polished materials, its design is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.",
    5560404: "An intense yet understated suit of heavy armor that strikes fear into the hearts of one's foes. This refined masterwork is made from a variety of valuable materials, sparing nothing to achieve excellence in both defense and mobility. Crafted using polished materials, it is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    5560405: "An intense yet understated suit of heavy armor that strikes fear into the hearts of one's foes. This refined masterwork is made from a variety of valuable materials, sparing nothing to achieve excellence in both defense and mobility. Crafted using polished materials, it is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.\n\nA message is engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5560406: "Luxurious heavy armor tailored for veteran knights. The thick fabric pads the wearer's body against sharp, striking blows. Crafted using polished materials, its design is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.\n\nAs this item is a rental, you cannot perform any action that changes its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, talk to the NPC you rented it from.",
    5560407: "Luxurious heavy armor tailored for veteran knights. The thick fabric pads the wearer's body against sharp, striking blows. Crafted using polished materials, its design is sized to comfortably fit combatants of all races.\n\nA message is engraved on it.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
