    5600001: "Dream Catcher of Blossoming Memories",
    5600002: "A one-handed sword imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    5600007: "A shuriken imbued with the warmth of Blaanid's caring heart.\nFashioned with a Forget-me-not motif that reminds you of Blaanid.\n(Cannot be upgraded, enchanted, reforged, or traded)",
    5600008: "A throwing weapon wielded by agents of shadow who carry out their missions in sprawling cities where colored lights hold even the dark of night at bay. Its soft glow will illuminate even the dimmest corridors.",
    5600009: "A spellbook imbued with a transcendent power capable of setting free souls in bondage. In skilled hands, the dynamic energies coursing through it can be released to explosive effect.",
    5600010: "A shuriken imbued with a transcendent power capable of setting free souls in bondage. In skilled hands, the dynamic energies coursing through it can be released to explosive effect.",
    5600011: "Hound of Winter's Longbow",
    5600012: "Inventory Expansion Coupon",
    5600013: "A staff containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons. An aura of darkness emanates from it like a stormcloud.\n\nAs this weapon is a rental, you cannot perform any action that would change its attributes, such as trading, enchanting, or upgrading it. To remove this item from your inventory, speak with the NPC you rented it from.",
    5600017: "Special Troubadour's Waistcoat (M)",
    5600018: "A cylinder fashioned in the likeness of a similar implement possessed by a goddess. It greatly enhances the effects of elemental Alchemy skills.",
    5600019: "A pair of steel control bars fashioned in the likeness of those possessed by a goddess. The precision control they afford allows their wielder to render enemies helpless.",
    5600020: "Celtic Druid Staff (Event)",
    5600021: "Perseus Swift Shuriken (Event)",
    5600022: "Celtic Throwing Star (Event)",
    5600023: "Nightbringer Wraith Chain Blade (Event)",
    5600024: "Perseus Rending Chain Blade (Event)",
    5600025: "Celtic Howling Chain Blade (Event)",
    5600026: "Nightbringer Vanguard Shield (Event)",
    5600027: "Perseus Vigilant Shield (Event)",
    5600028: "A Chain Blade fashioned in the likeness of one possessed by a goddess. Honed blades embedded in a durable chain render it capable of shredding enemies with whiplike reach and flexibility.",
    5600029: "Arrows containing a fragment of a great power that has crystallized over the course of eons.",
    5600030: "Steward of Secrets Greatsword",
    5600031: "파도의 수호자 가발(여성용)",
    5600036: "A pair of diaphanous wings woven from sheer fabric and trimmed with beautiful lace. A mysterious power rests lightly upon its delicate threads, like dew on a spider's web.\n(Dyeable)",
    5600037: "선명한 마법진 날개",
    5600038: "진노한 마법진 날개",
    5600039: "초연한 마법진 날개",
    5600040: "차분한 마법진 날개",
    5600041: "고고한 마법진 날개",
    5600042: "진노한 마법진 날개",
    5600046: "An advanced support puppet whose design is based on descriptions of Targon, one of the dragon twins said to have assumed human form to walk among mankind. Cannot be equipped with other flying puppets. When you enter a mission or dungeon, it can reveal the layout on the mini-map, tell you which marble will open a door, cast a magic shield to protect you, or automatically use potions based on the conditions you set.",
    5600050: "우아한 에이더 레이븐 윙",
    5600053: "Festival Sneakers (F)",
    5600054: "A casual and comfy bandana with a festive look. Perfect to keep sweat out of your eyes during the most thrilling of events!",
    5600055: "A casual and boyish outfit featuring jeans and a denim jacket. Someone has covered it with colorful doodles.",
    5600056: "판 캐릭터 프린트 의상(남성용)",
    5600062: "A stylish pair of men's shoes produced by the Bleugenne brand, featuring a luxurious design and top-quality materials.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600063: "A pair of durable boots fit for one tasked with tending the greenery and hedgerows of a whimsical garden. Fashioned from treated leather, they protect the wearer's feet on soft dirt paths and rocky roads alike.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600064: "A pair of comfortable shoes fit for one tasked with tending the greenery and hedgerows of a whimsical garden. Fashioned from treated leather, they protect the wearer's feet on soft dirt paths and rocky roads alike.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600065: "A pair of shoes that give your toes all the breathing room they need. The rabbit logo on the back makes a stylish statement while you're on the go.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600066: "A pair of heels that look refined at first glance but have a rugged edge to them.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600067: "Fearsome greaves worn by the ruler of a dark kingdom. Foes shall known them all too well when they are trodden underfoot.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600068: "Ornate sandals worn by a saint blessed by angels. Wherever the wearer walks, blessings shall spring up in their wake.\n\nThese clothes can be equipped during the 'A Valentine's Glow-up' event period, but will expire every Thursday at 7:00 AM (Server Time).",
    5600069: "A uniform worn by the maids of the noble house of Elysees. Sewn with ruffles and lace aplenty, this dress gives serving ladies an air both proper and playful, as favored by their aristocratic employer. Wearing this outfit allows you to strike a special pose.",
    5600070: "Wiggling Studded Cat Eared Headband",
