    5700004: "A pair of gloves for a keen witness who observes the world. Protective and supportive, they're a necessity for a safe trip.",
    5700008: "A romantic, refined hairstyle that's formal without being fussy. A slight natural wave elevates the look.",
    5700009: "Dignified Crazy Rich Milletian Wear (M) (Tolly's Fashion)",
    5700015: "Special Livestream Star Wear (M)",
    5700018: "Wild West Gunslinger Gloves (M)",
    5700021: "A wig with a style that exudes elegance with a hint of the picaresque. The hair tied back in a long tail calls to mind the dashing dancers and duelists of old.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
    5700022: "A wig styled in a fashion favored among the emissaries charged with escorting souls from this world to the next.\n(This item will be deleted automatically when the event ends.)",
