    5700038: "Circus Performer's Gloves (F) (Rental)",
    5700044: "A pair of leather bracers much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, they boast improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.\n\nA message is tooled into one.\n<color=1>I hope this aids you as you journey across Erinn.</color>",
    5700047: "A pair of shoes much beloved by those with an interest in archery. Fashioned from higher-end materials, they boast improved performance over the basic version, allowing the wearer to draw out greater power when using a bow.",
    5700048: "Saint Guardian's Helmet (M)",
    5700050: "A pair of cloth wraps tied around the wrists, embodying the spirit of a young man who appreciates the finer things amidst the excited atmosphere of a festival. The knotted cord that keeps them cinched adds to the traditional aesthetic.",
    5700053: "윈터 캐주얼 가발(남성용)",
    5700055: "붉은 구름의 매 상자",
    5700057: "Special Trendy Day Tripper Wear (F)",
    5700058: "Special Lovely Day Tripper Wear (M)",
    5700060: "전통을 넘어, 새로운 리듬으로. 히트 비트 스쿨 유니폼은 활기찬 번화가 중심지의 스트리트 감성을 잘 표현한 교복이다. 입으면 특별한 모션을 취할 수 있다.",
    5700061: "Taillteann Townspeople Doll Bag Box",
    5700062: "Taillteann Townspeople Doll Bag Box",
    5700067: "롭 이어 토끼 귀 모양의 머리띠. 움직이는 귀가 매력적이다.",
    5700068: "A pair of shoes as refined as function-first footwear can be, provided to those granted membership in one of the kingdom's Royal Societies. Their design conceals a steel plate in the toes that protect the wearer's feet from any fumbled objects.",
